1
00:00:01,671 --> 00:00:09,809
♪♪

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Imetasfiriwa na Msovu

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Tembelea Tovuti Yetu Ya Swahili Subtitles

4
00:00:09,844 --> 00:00:18,191
♪♪

5
00:00:18,226 --> 00:00:26,364
♪♪

6
00:00:26,399 --> 00:00:34,537
♪♪

7
00:00:34,572 --> 00:00:42,710
♪♪

8
00:00:42,745 --> 00:00:46,186
-Nawaza kuhusu
hatua kubwa ya ajabu

9
00:00:46,221 --> 00:00:50,586
iliyowezeshwa na
maendeleo ya mawasiliano,

10
00:00:50,621 --> 00:00:53,589
hususan transista
na zaidi ya yote,

11
00:00:53,624 --> 00:00:56,295
satelaiti ya mawasiliano.

12
00:00:56,330 --> 00:00:58,561
Mambo haya
yatawezesha ulimwengu

13
00:00:58,596 --> 00:01:01,399
ambapo tunaweza kuwasiliana
papo hapo,

14
00:01:01,434 --> 00:01:04,567
popote pale tulipo.

15
00:01:04,602 --> 00:01:06,734
Itawezekana katika enzi hiyo,

16
00:01:06,769 --> 00:01:08,835
pengine miaka 50 tu kuanzia sasa,

17
00:01:08,870 --> 00:01:13,675
kwa mtu kuendesha
biashara yake akiwa Tahiti au Bali

18
00:01:13,710 --> 00:01:17,382
vizuri kama ambavyo
angefanya akiwa London.

19
00:01:17,417 --> 00:01:19,450
Kwa hakika,
ikibainika kuwa na manufaa,

20
00:01:19,485 --> 00:01:22,189
karibu kila ujuzi wa kiuongozi,

21
00:01:22,224 --> 00:01:24,224
ujuzi wowote wa kiutawala,

22
00:01:24,259 --> 00:01:26,226
hata ujuzi wowote wa kimwili,

23
00:01:26,261 --> 00:01:30,230
utaweza kufanyika
bila kuzuiliwa na umbali.

24
00:01:30,265 --> 00:01:31,858
Wakati huo utakapofika,

25
00:01:31,893 --> 00:01:34,630
ulimwengu mzima utakuwa
umesinyaa hadi kuwa nukta.

26
00:01:34,665 --> 00:01:37,303
Na jukumu la kiasili
la mji

27
00:01:37,338 --> 00:01:39,503
kama sehemu ya kukutania kwa binadamu

28
00:01:39,538 --> 00:01:42,737
lingekuwa limeacha kuwa na
maana yoyote.

29
00:01:42,772 --> 00:01:45,641
Kiuhalisia, watu
hawatakuwa wakisafiri tena kwenda kazini.

30
00:01:45,676 --> 00:01:47,412
Watawasiliana.

31
00:01:47,447 --> 00:01:52,450
♪♪

32
00:01:52,485 --> 00:01:58,522
♪♪

33
00:01:58,557 --> 00:02:00,821
-Lahaula!
-Hatujachelewa!

34
00:02:00,856 --> 00:02:02,757
-Hapana, najua,
lakini nataka kutapika.

35
00:02:02,792 --> 00:02:04,561
-Sawa.

36
00:02:11,999 --> 00:02:13,834
Ala!

37
00:02:23,978 --> 00:02:27,419
<i>-Matt Sundin ndiye mlegevu zaidi</i>
<i>kati ya wote huko nje.</i>

38
00:02:27,454 --> 00:02:31,192
<i>Amethibitisha kuwa na kipaji katika NHL lakini</i>
<i>hafungi mabao kama Leafs wanavyohitaji --</i>

39
00:02:44,999 --> 00:02:46,966
-Mgeni wako wa saa tatu amefika.
-Brock yuko wapi?

40
00:02:47,001 --> 00:02:48,737
-Ofisini kwake.
-Bwana Balsillie?

41
00:02:48,772 --> 00:02:51,443
Ulitaka kuona ripoti hii.
-Zungumza na Shelly.

42
00:03:08,858 --> 00:03:11,430
-[Akinong'ona]
Saketi jumuishi...

43
00:03:11,465 --> 00:03:13,828
-Naam, hatimaye nimeelewa
nukuu ile,

44
00:03:13,863 --> 00:03:16,633
Unapokuwa mtu mzima,
moyo wako hufa.

45
00:03:19,605 --> 00:03:22,375
Hiyo inatoka kwenye "Breakfast Club."
John Hughes.

46
00:03:22,410 --> 00:03:23,937
-Unasikia hiyo?

47
00:03:23,972 --> 00:03:26,874
[Mlio hafifu]

48
00:03:26,909 --> 00:03:29,712
-Ee, naam.

49
00:03:29,747 --> 00:03:31,549
Unazungumzia ule mvumo?
-Mmh.

50
00:03:31,584 --> 00:03:34,354
-Ni ofisi, nina hakika wana
mivumo mingi midogo midogo.

51
00:03:34,389 --> 00:03:35,982
-Mm.
-Ni mlio fulani hafifu.

52
00:03:41,825 --> 00:03:44,991
-Hapo.
-Umeugundua.

53
00:03:45,026 --> 00:03:49,028
-Mm.
-Nini?

54
00:03:49,063 --> 00:03:53,670
Imetengenezwa Uchina --
alama ya mnyama?

55
00:03:57,940 --> 00:04:02,041
[Mlio wa kukwaruza]
Aa... Ee...

56
00:04:02,076 --> 00:04:03,812
Mike?
-Siwezi kutulia.

57
00:04:03,847 --> 00:04:05,715
-Kwani nini?
Je, utarekebisha hili?

58
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:08,751
-Nitalirekebisha.
-Aa, sasa hivi siyo wakati wake.

59
00:04:08,786 --> 00:04:10,687
Mkutano unaanza baada ya,
kama dakika mbili hivi.

60
00:04:10,722 --> 00:04:11,919
Sasa hivi siyo wakati wake.
Sasa hivi siyo wakati wake.

61
00:04:11,954 --> 00:04:13,327
Sasa hivi siyo wakati wake.
-Sawa?

62
00:04:13,362 --> 00:04:14,922
Nahitaji, kama, kibanio cha karatasi.

63
00:04:14,957 --> 00:04:18,926
-Hayo ni mambo ya kiume tu.
Hayo ni mambo ya kijinga ya kiume.

64
00:04:22,030 --> 00:04:24,635
-Haina swichi ya kuzimia.
Inamaanisha inawaka wakati wote.

65
00:04:24,670 --> 00:04:26,868
Kwa hiyo inatoa tu mlio kila wakati.
-Eeeh. Ndiyo.

66
00:04:26,903 --> 00:04:31,004
Ee... Basi,

67
00:04:31,039 --> 00:04:34,876
Ndiyo, nenda haraka.

68
00:04:34,911 --> 00:04:36,647
-Unaweza kumwambia kuwa
hatapata -- [anacheka] --

69
00:04:36,682 --> 00:04:38,946
Hatapata chuma.

70
00:04:38,981 --> 00:04:41,949
Mchanganyiko wa madini, Harry!

71
00:04:41,984 --> 00:04:44,754
Nitakupigia baadaye.

72
00:04:44,789 --> 00:04:47,592
-Wako nje.

73
00:04:47,627 --> 00:04:49,792
-Hawa watu ni
Waholanzi kweli, au?

74
00:04:49,827 --> 00:04:52,663
-[Anacheka]

75
00:04:52,698 --> 00:04:56,436
Sikiliza, Rick, nimefikiria
sana kuhusu hili.

76
00:04:56,471 --> 00:04:58,834
Na kama hawa jamaa watakubali makubaliano haya,

77
00:04:58,869 --> 00:05:01,067
nataka kuongoza kitengo hiki kipya.

78
00:05:12,113 --> 00:05:14,652
-Unadhani unaweza kuongoza mahali hapa?

79
00:05:14,687 --> 00:05:17,589
-Ndiyo! Ndiyo!

80
00:05:17,624 --> 00:05:18,986
-Mimi pia.

81
00:05:22,024 --> 00:05:26,158
Ili tuwe na uelewa mmoja,
kama jambo hili halitafanikiwa,

82
00:05:26,193 --> 00:05:29,436
hatukuwahi kufanya mazungumzo haya.

83
00:05:29,471 --> 00:05:31,570
-Safi. Safi sana. Hmm...

84
00:05:34,608 --> 00:05:36,377
-Asante.

85
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:40,744
-Kuna marekebisho moja.

86
00:05:40,779 --> 00:05:42,108
Inaonekana Wamarekani
waliwapa

87
00:05:42,143 --> 00:05:44,616
mpango fulani wa kisasa wa mgawanyo wa kodi,

88
00:05:44,651 --> 00:05:47,553
hivyo tunapaswa kuwaonyesha
toleo la Kanada.

89
00:05:47,588 --> 00:05:48,851
-Sina hiyo.
-Hapana, hapana.

90
00:05:48,886 --> 00:05:50,424
-Callahan aliandaa
kitu dakika za mwisho.

91
00:05:50,459 --> 00:05:54,461
Tutamleta hapa
aili akielezee.

92
00:05:54,496 --> 00:05:57,794
-Callahan.
Hmm...

93
00:05:57,829 --> 00:06:00,060
Unajua nini?
Nadhani hilo ni wazo baya.

94
00:06:00,095 --> 00:06:02,964
-Kwa nini?

95
00:06:02,999 --> 00:06:05,670
-Sikiliza, Rick,
kwa nini usimwombe

96
00:06:05,705 --> 00:06:07,067
Callahan anielezee
hilo suala la kodi

97
00:06:07,102 --> 00:06:08,673
nami nitalijumuisha -- nitalijumuisha
kwenye wasilisho langu.

98
00:06:08,708 --> 00:06:11,038
Nadhani hiyo ni bora zaidi.
-Kyle alikesha usiku kucha

99
00:06:11,073 --> 00:06:13,172
akiandaa jambo hili
kama hisani kwangu.

100
00:06:13,207 --> 00:06:17,616
Yeye ndiye atakayewasilisha.
-Rick, namaanisha...

101
00:06:17,651 --> 00:06:19,816
Unampanga huyu jamaa
amfanyie Stork wasilisho?

102
00:06:19,851 --> 00:06:25,118
Namaanisha, anaonekana kama...
mpumbavu, mjinga kabisa.

103
00:06:25,153 --> 00:06:28,528
-Jim...
Sikuulizi.

104
00:06:28,563 --> 00:06:36,668
♪♪

105
00:06:36,703 --> 00:06:38,604
-Haya, safi sana.

106
00:06:38,639 --> 00:06:44,137
♪♪

107
00:06:44,172 --> 00:06:47,943
-Haya. Mwanaume mwenye upara, mwenye sura ya kutisha
anatuelekea sasa hivi.

108
00:06:47,978 --> 00:06:50,011
-Lahaula!
-Mike?

109
00:06:50,046 --> 00:06:51,782
-Ndiyo. Nimeelewa.

110
00:06:53,654 --> 00:06:55,555
-Kaa chonjo!
-Loh, jamani.

111
00:06:55,590 --> 00:06:57,018
Keti chini. Keti chini.

112
00:06:58,824 --> 00:07:00,857
-Afadhali hivi.

113
00:07:05,798 --> 00:07:08,502
-[Anashusha pumzi]

114
00:07:16,303 --> 00:07:18,105
-Ndiyo. Nikusaidie nini?

115
00:07:18,140 --> 00:07:19,843
-Ndiyo. Habari.

116
00:07:19,878 --> 00:07:25,244
Mimi ni Mike Lazaridis,
Mkurugenzi Mkuu wa Research in Motion.

117
00:07:25,279 --> 00:07:27,279
Tunatengeneza mifumo mbalimbali
ya vifaa vya kompyuta

118
00:07:27,314 --> 00:07:29,853
tukitumia sakiti jumuishi
zenye muundo maalum,

119
00:07:29,888 --> 00:07:31,525
pamoja na vipengele vinavyopatikana
sokoni kwa urahisi

120
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,989
vinavyotolewa na wauzaji wakubwa wa vifaa
kama vile Intel,

121
00:07:34,024 --> 00:07:36,563
American Micro Devices
na CYRIX.

122
00:07:36,598 --> 00:07:39,192
Wateja wetu wamejumuisha
US Robotics,

123
00:07:39,227 --> 00:07:41,095
Rogers Cantel, RAM Mobile.

124
00:07:41,130 --> 00:07:42,734
-Subiri kidogo.

125
00:07:42,769 --> 00:07:44,032
[Anapiga simu]

126
00:07:49,809 --> 00:07:52,975
Hujambo, wewe ndiye unayeshughulikia dawati la Callahan, sivyo?

127
00:07:53,010 --> 00:07:55,010
Sawa, vyema sana. Huyu ni Jim Balsillie.

128
00:07:55,045 --> 00:07:57,243
Brock alitaka nifanye uhakiki wa haraka wa mambo yale ya kodi

129
00:07:57,278 --> 00:08:00,917
kabla ya mkutano. Unaweza kuniletea --

130
00:08:00,952 --> 00:08:02,655
Kabisa.

131
00:08:02,690 --> 00:08:04,250
Sawa, vyema. Ahsante.

132
00:08:12,799 --> 00:08:15,899
Sawa, hiki ni nini?

133
00:08:15,934 --> 00:08:20,871
-Basi, tulikuwa na mwalimu wa ufundi...

134
00:08:20,906 --> 00:08:22,972
aliyetuambia -- ohoo, tulikuwa na mwalimu wa ufundi

135
00:08:23,007 --> 00:08:24,908
katika shule ya upili aliyeitwa Bwana Moshinsky,

136
00:08:24,943 --> 00:08:28,274
aliyetuambia kuwa mtu atakayeweka kompyuta ndani ya simu

137
00:08:28,309 --> 00:08:30,914
ataubadilisha ulimwengu.

138
00:08:30,949 --> 00:08:32,311
Sasa, tuna mpango wa kutumia

139
00:08:32,346 --> 00:08:35,083
upana wa mawimbi ya UHF yasiyotumika

140
00:08:35,118 --> 00:08:37,591
kutengeneza kifaa kimoja cha mkononi chenye kila kitu.

141
00:08:37,626 --> 00:08:39,021
[Mlio]
-Msaidizi wa Adam Callahan

142
00:08:39,056 --> 00:08:41,793
yupo hapa kukuona?
-Mwambie aingie.

143
00:08:43,797 --> 00:08:46,127
Vyema.
-Samahani, Bwana Balsillie.

144
00:08:46,162 --> 00:08:48,129
Sikutambua kuwa ulihitaji nakala ya

145
00:08:48,164 --> 00:08:50,329
ripoti hii ya kodi pia --
-Niko kwenye mkutano sasa hivi.

146
00:08:55,237 --> 00:08:57,006
Sawa.

147
00:09:01,683 --> 00:09:06,752
-Basi, kimsingi kuna mawimbi ya bure

148
00:09:06,787 --> 00:09:10,151
ya mtandao yasiyo na waya kote Amerika ya Kaskazini,

149
00:09:10,186 --> 00:09:13,924
na hakuna yeyote aliyegundua jinsi ya kuyatumia.

150
00:09:13,959 --> 00:09:17,026
Kuna mtandao wa bure ndani ya chumba hiki sasa hivi.

151
00:09:17,061 --> 00:09:20,326
-Naam.

152
00:09:20,361 --> 00:09:24,066
-Ni kama zile nguvu za asili.

153
00:09:24,101 --> 00:09:25,837
Samahani. Je, umewahi kuiona
filamu ya "Vita vya Nyota"?

154
00:09:28,039 --> 00:09:30,776
-Hapana.

155
00:09:30,811 --> 00:09:34,340
-Basi, piga picha kifaa cha kupokea ujumbe,

156
00:09:34,375 --> 00:09:39,345
simu ya mkononi na mashine ya barua
pepe, vyote katika kitu kimoja.

157
00:09:45,991 --> 00:09:49,795
-Tunakiita, mhm, Kiunganishi cha Mfukoni.

158
00:09:55,429 --> 00:09:59,365
-Sawa, sikiliza, hatufanyi
mambo ya namna hiyo hapa.

159
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:01,708
Sisi ni kampuni ya kibiashara
ya utengenezaji bidhaa.

160
00:10:01,743 --> 00:10:04,073
Unataka kuzungumza
na mwekezaji wa mitaji?

161
00:10:11,016 --> 00:10:13,049
Na unahitaji jina bora zaidi.

162
00:10:20,861 --> 00:10:23,125
-Unataka kulia?! Mike!

163
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:25,457
Oho, ni kukatishwa tamaa tu?
-Ndiyo.

164
00:10:25,492 --> 00:10:28,900
-Ulifanya vizuri sana!
-[Anasafisha koo]

165
00:10:28,935 --> 00:10:33,135
Naam, niliona kwamba Rick alituma gari la kifahari kuwafuata.

166
00:10:33,170 --> 00:10:35,940
Inaonekana tunahitaji muungano huu zaidi kuliko nilivyodhani.

167
00:10:35,975 --> 00:10:39,075
[Kicheko kidogo]

168
00:10:39,110 --> 00:10:40,813
Basi, najua tuna mengi
ya kuzungumzia,

169
00:10:40,848 --> 00:10:45,785
lakini nilifikiri tuanze
na mkakati wetu wa kodi.

170
00:10:45,820 --> 00:10:48,953
Sasa, nina hakika mlishasikia
kutoka kwa Wamarekani,

171
00:10:48,988 --> 00:10:51,219
lakini naomba niwahakikishie,
sisi pia tunajua jinsi ya

172
00:10:51,254 --> 00:10:53,188
kukwepa kodi hapa nchini Kanada.

173
00:10:53,223 --> 00:10:55,729
Sawa?

174
00:10:55,764 --> 00:10:57,159
Hivi ndivyo tunavyoweza kufanya:

175
00:10:57,194 --> 00:10:59,161
Tunalipa mishahara kupitia jimbo la Ontario,

176
00:10:59,196 --> 00:11:01,064
lakini tunawalipa wasambazaji wetu wote
kutoka Uholanzi.

177
00:11:01,099 --> 00:11:02,461
Tulikigawa hicho kitu
kati kwa kati kabisa.

178
00:11:02,496 --> 00:11:05,233
Upande wa kushoto hautajua
kile upande wa kulia unafanya.

179
00:11:05,268 --> 00:11:07,433
Pia, tunapata marupurupu
mazuri ya mkoa

180
00:11:07,468 --> 00:11:09,336
kama asante kwenye nguvu kazi ya uzalishaji.

181
00:11:09,371 --> 00:11:11,305
Tunapata punguzo kubwa
la kodi ya serikali kuu

182
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:14,341
kwa sababu hawajui kama
ni wa sekta binafsi au ya umma.

183
00:11:14,376 --> 00:11:23,152
♪♪

184
00:11:23,187 --> 00:11:32,359
♪♪

185
00:11:32,394 --> 00:11:35,868
-Nivute melini!

186
00:11:35,903 --> 00:11:39,333
-Mfungwa, aliyeshikiliwa
ndani ya ulimwengu wa kidijitali wa

187
00:11:39,368 --> 00:11:41,203
kompyuta yenyewe.

188
00:11:41,238 --> 00:11:43,007
♪ Ukisafiri juu ya wimbi lolote ♪

189
00:11:43,042 --> 00:11:44,976
♪ Hiyo ndiyo bahati unayoitamani ♪

190
00:11:45,011 --> 00:11:46,912
♪ Hawaiamini sasa hivi ♪

191
00:11:46,947 --> 00:11:48,947
♪ Wanadhani tu ni upuuzi ♪

192
00:11:48,982 --> 00:11:50,949
♪ Basi, una chochote? ♪

193
00:11:50,984 --> 00:11:52,819
♪ Yeyote angeweza kufanya ♪

194
00:11:52,854 --> 00:11:54,480
♪ Nani ambaye angejali kabisa ♪

195
00:11:54,515 --> 00:11:57,054
♪ Sio wewe ♪

196
00:11:57,089 --> 00:11:59,485
♪ Moyo mwingine ♪
-Hujambo?

197
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:01,421
-Habari!
-♪ Umefanya biashara ♪

198
00:12:01,456 --> 00:12:03,896
♪ Isahau, isahau ♪
-Kwa hiyo, unachosema ni kwamba

199
00:12:03,931 --> 00:12:05,931
unagusa na kuongea tu?
-♪ Sielewi ♪

200
00:12:05,966 --> 00:12:08,098
♪ Jinsi moyo ulivyo piki ♪

201
00:12:08,133 --> 00:12:12,300
♪ Lakini kwa namna fulani uhusiano
muhimu unafanyika ♪

202
00:12:12,335 --> 00:12:15,534
-Unaweza kutumia simu yako ya mkononi
kuniagizia piza.

203
00:12:15,569 --> 00:12:17,877
-Na hiyo inajumuisha
dakika 50 za muda wa maongezi.

204
00:12:17,912 --> 00:12:20,374
-Tutakuarifu.
-Vema, ni jambo la kisasa sana kuwa

205
00:12:20,409 --> 00:12:23,916
kwenye mtandao hivi sasa.
-[Wote wanapiga kelele]

206
00:12:23,951 --> 00:12:25,511
-Bado ninaamini
Apple ina mustakabali.

207
00:12:25,546 --> 00:12:28,514
Njia ya kutokea si kupunguza na
kuharibu, ni kuvumbua.

208
00:12:28,549 --> 00:12:30,318
♪ Tukipanda juu ya chochote ♪

209
00:12:30,353 --> 00:12:32,122
♪ Chochote kinafaa tu ♪

210
00:12:32,157 --> 00:12:34,091
♪ Nani angefikiria jambo kama hilo ♪

211
00:12:34,126 --> 00:12:35,158
[Anafunga breki ya maegesho]

212
00:12:35,193 --> 00:12:37,127
-Ooh, sawa. Haya ndiyo mawazo yangu.

213
00:12:37,162 --> 00:12:39,998
Mike, ni rahisi sana.
Mpe habari njema,

214
00:12:40,033 --> 00:12:42,935
kisha mbaya --
utaratibu wa habari njema na mbaya.

215
00:12:42,970 --> 00:12:46,972
Sawa? Utasema
njema -- Mike?!

216
00:12:47,007 --> 00:12:50,008
Nini?

217
00:12:50,043 --> 00:12:51,405
Kila kitu kitakuwa sawa.

218
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:53,275
Bado tuna
mkataba wa US Robotics.

219
00:12:53,310 --> 00:12:55,541
Sisi ni kama, pango lilisema
nini kuhusu Aladdin,

220
00:12:55,576 --> 00:12:57,213
"Almasi isiyong'arishwa"?
Lahaula!

221
00:12:57,248 --> 00:13:01,151
-Nini?
-Nimesahau stendi ya picha.

222
00:13:01,186 --> 00:13:03,252
-Hapana, lazima tubadilishe jina.
Bidhaa inahitaji jina jipya.

223
00:13:03,287 --> 00:13:05,089
-Unampa mtu huyo
sifa nyingi kupita kiasi, rafiki.

224
00:13:05,124 --> 00:13:07,157
Hajaona "Vita vya Nyota."
Ana kipara.

225
00:13:07,192 --> 00:13:10,457
Unataka kubashiri kiasi gani kwamba
hawatataja hata simu hiyo.

226
00:13:10,492 --> 00:13:14,065
[Kuandika, kicheko]

227
00:13:14,100 --> 00:13:16,331
-Je, wewe ndiye baba wa ofisi?
-[Kicheko]

228
00:13:16,366 --> 00:13:20,071
-Ndugu. Sawa.
Tengeneza -- tengeneza kitu.

229
00:13:20,106 --> 00:13:22,238
Tengeneza "Scott ni hovyo" --
-Siwezi.

230
00:13:22,273 --> 00:13:25,439
Ndio maana natumia
kompyuta yako.

231
00:13:25,474 --> 00:13:27,507
-Kijana 21 Kanada.

232
00:13:27,542 --> 00:13:29,883
-Ndiye mimi.

233
00:13:29,918 --> 00:13:32,380
Huyu jamaa ananiambia
kuhusu kunusa --

234
00:13:32,415 --> 00:13:34,514
Kunusa --
[Mlango unafunguka]

235
00:13:36,650 --> 00:13:38,419
-Je, wameinunua ile simu?

236
00:13:40,654 --> 00:13:44,425
-Basi, tuna habari njema
na habari mbaya.

237
00:13:48,332 --> 00:13:51,069
Ile -- sawa,
habari mbaya ni kwamba,

238
00:13:51,104 --> 00:13:55,040
ndiyo, kwenye uwasilishaji ule,
hatukusikilizwa,

239
00:13:55,075 --> 00:13:57,306
na hawakuielewa
bidhaa hiyo,

240
00:13:57,341 --> 00:13:59,506
na hivyo
hawakuinunua simu hiyo.

241
00:14:02,247 --> 00:14:06,447
-Habari njema ilikuwa gani?
-Habari njema ni ipi?

242
00:14:06,482 --> 00:14:10,319
-Usiku wa dharura wa filamu,
sasa hivi, ya Steven Spielberg,

243
00:14:10,354 --> 00:14:13,927
"Wavamizi wa Sanduku Lililopotea,"
mfumo wa skrini pana.

244
00:14:13,962 --> 00:14:16,424
-Haiwezekani!
-Nawahi mbele. Nawahi. Nawahi.

245
00:14:16,459 --> 00:14:19,295
Nawahi!

246
00:14:19,330 --> 00:14:21,231
-Ulisema pambo lao la kichwa
lilikuwa na alama upande mmoja tu.

247
00:14:21,266 --> 00:14:23,299
Je, una uhakika kabisa?

248
00:14:25,006 --> 00:14:27,468
Fimbo ya Balloq ni ndefu mno.

249
00:14:27,503 --> 00:14:29,943
[Wote] "Tunachimba mahali
pisipo sahihi"!

250
00:14:29,978 --> 00:14:32,242
[Kicheko]

251
00:14:32,277 --> 00:14:34,343
[Muziki wa kusisimua]

252
00:14:34,378 --> 00:14:35,949
-Usifanye hivyo!

253
00:14:40,219 --> 00:14:43,319
-[Wote] "Miadi mibaya."
-Miadi mibaya.

254
00:14:43,354 --> 00:14:46,619
-Miadi kadhaa mibaya.
-Miadi kadhaa mibaya!

255
00:14:46,654 --> 00:14:49,490
Miadi kadhaa mibaya!
-Hiyo ilikuwa -- hiyo ilikuwa hapo.

256
00:14:49,525 --> 00:14:52,493
Kwa nini walienda upande mwingine?
Hiyo ilikuwa kama vile...

257
00:14:52,528 --> 00:14:57,267
♪♪

258
00:14:57,302 --> 00:15:01,139
-Mike, unakosa
filamu uipendayo, rafiki!

259
00:15:01,174 --> 00:15:07,607
♪♪

260
00:15:07,642 --> 00:15:14,284
♪♪

261
00:15:14,319 --> 00:15:20,752
♪♪

262
00:15:20,787 --> 00:15:27,429
♪♪

263
00:15:27,464 --> 00:15:30,696
-[Anashusha pumzi]

264
00:15:30,731 --> 00:15:39,045
♪♪

265
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:47,152
♪♪

266
00:15:47,187 --> 00:15:50,716
<i>-Toronto wanashinda kwa matokeo</i>
<i>ya tano kwa nne.</i>

267
00:15:50,751 --> 00:15:53,191
<i>Doug Gilmour anaongeza pasi tatu za mabao</i>
<i>kwenye tano alizokuwa nazo</i>

268
00:15:53,226 --> 00:15:55,490
<i>kumaliza mchezo akiwa na thelathini....</i>

269
00:15:55,525 --> 00:15:57,096
<i>...katika kipindi cha ziada.</i>

270
00:15:57,131 --> 00:15:59,296
<i>Lakini ni wazi simulizi ilikuwa --</i>

271
00:15:59,331 --> 00:16:01,100
[Anazima injini]

272
00:16:01,135 --> 00:16:02,563
-Wako juu au chini kushoto?

273
00:16:02,598 --> 00:16:04,367
-Nenda, nina kundi langu lote.

274
00:16:04,402 --> 00:16:05,731
-Tuma -- Tuma kila kitu.
Juu kushoto.

275
00:16:05,766 --> 00:16:07,535
Hebu tuchukue.
Hebu tucheze kamari.

276
00:16:07,570 --> 00:16:09,504
Tutamfuata Scott.
-Kuna yeyote mwenye

277
00:16:09,539 --> 00:16:11,506
waya wa mawasiliano wa aina ya 'c'?
-Hata hawajui

278
00:16:11,541 --> 00:16:13,772
Hata siko upande wa juu kushoto.
-Scott, unanishambulia.

279
00:16:13,807 --> 00:16:15,411
-Nini?
-Unanishambulia.

280
00:16:15,446 --> 00:16:17,611
-Oh, samahani.
-Wafungulie mbwa, Ethan,

281
00:16:17,646 --> 00:16:19,547
Wafungulie mbwa.
Wanakuja kwa kasi.

282
00:16:19,582 --> 00:16:21,549
-Chini kulia.
-Namtuma mwingine. Mwingine.

283
00:16:21,584 --> 00:16:23,287
-Wana makombora.
Lazima nishuke chini.

284
00:16:23,322 --> 00:16:25,223
-Kuna yeyote mwenye
nyaya za mawasiliano za aina ya 'c'?

285
00:16:25,258 --> 00:16:28,226
-Iage hiyo!
-Oh, pistoni inasogea!

286
00:16:28,261 --> 00:16:30,162
-Hapana!
-Pistoni inasogea!

287
00:16:30,197 --> 00:16:34,100
Ndugu, hebu fanya kweli.
[Simu inalia]

288
00:16:34,135 --> 00:16:36,069
-Hapana! Hapana!
[Mshindo]

289
00:16:36,104 --> 00:16:38,665
-Aa! Aa!

290
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:41,602
-Oh!
-Samahani, vijana!

291
00:16:41,637 --> 00:16:45,606
Lakini imerudi!
Imerudi!

292
00:16:45,641 --> 00:16:48,081
-Ulikuwa umewakamata --
-Imerudi!

293
00:16:48,116 --> 00:16:50,248
-[Anakohoa kidogo]

294
00:16:57,455 --> 00:16:59,686
-Asante.
-Asante sana.

295
00:16:59,721 --> 00:17:01,655
-Sihitaji chochote.
Asante.

296
00:17:01,690 --> 00:17:03,855
Hivyo najua
jinsi ya kuuza simu yako.

297
00:17:03,890 --> 00:17:07,166
Najua jinsi ya kuitangaza, na najua
tunaweza kumwuzia nani.

298
00:17:07,201 --> 00:17:11,467
-Nani?
-Unamaanisha nini unaposema, sisi?

299
00:17:11,502 --> 00:17:13,106
-Hivi ndivyo makubaliano yalivyo.

300
00:17:13,141 --> 00:17:15,240
Nitaacha kazi yangu
kule Sutherland Schultz.

301
00:17:15,275 --> 00:17:18,738
Ukinifanya kuwa Mkurugenzi Mkuu
wa kampuni ya Utafiti katika Mwendo.

302
00:17:21,248 --> 00:17:23,644
-Unaongea kwa dhati?

303
00:17:23,679 --> 00:17:26,548
-Hilo lilikuwa jaribio baya zaidi la ushawishi wa bidhaa
ambalo sijawahi kuona maishani mwangu.

304
00:17:26,583 --> 00:17:28,715
Ninyi hamna nafasi
yoyote huko nje.

305
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:30,816
Mnanihitaji mimi.

306
00:17:30,851 --> 00:17:34,226
-Samahani. Sijui unadhani
wewe ni nani,

307
00:17:34,261 --> 00:17:37,196
lakini tuko sawa kabisa.

308
00:17:37,231 --> 00:17:40,364
Tuna mkataba wa dola milioni kumi na sita
na kampuni ya Roboti za Marekani.

309
00:17:40,399 --> 00:17:42,828
-Milioni kumi na sita?
-Ndiyo, ni kweli.

310
00:17:42,863 --> 00:17:46,535
-Lo. Sawa.
Na walinunua nini?

311
00:17:46,570 --> 00:17:49,637
-Modemu.
Ushawahi kusikia habari zake?

312
00:17:49,672 --> 00:17:52,673
-Je, ni kama ile nguvu katika
filamu ya "Vita vya Nyota"?

313
00:17:52,708 --> 00:17:56,644
-Inachekesha sana. Unajua,
nembo yenu kimsingi ni SS.

314
00:17:56,679 --> 00:18:00,483
-Na wamewalipa kiasi gani
katika hizo dola milioni kumi na sita?

315
00:18:00,518 --> 00:18:02,551
-Ndiyo. Hakuna chochote.
-Sifuri?

316
00:18:02,586 --> 00:18:04,916
-Bado hakuna chochote.
Hatujawasilisha modemu bado.

317
00:18:04,951 --> 00:18:07,721
-Kweli, tuliwatumia sampuli za bidhaa miezi kadhaa iliyopita,

318
00:18:07,756 --> 00:18:10,724
na idara yao ya uhasibu
haitaki hata kurudisha

319
00:18:10,759 --> 00:18:12,429
simu zetu.
-Ndiyo, lakini wata —

320
00:18:12,464 --> 00:18:14,167
Kuna nini kinaendelea?
Watatulipa.

321
00:18:14,202 --> 00:18:16,268
Tuna mkataba wa dola milioni kumi na sita
na kampuni ya Roboti za Marekani.

322
00:18:16,303 --> 00:18:18,732
-Ndiyo, kwa hiyo, ninyi mnatapeliwa.

323
00:18:18,767 --> 00:18:21,702
-Kwa nini una— kwa nini unafikiri—
kwa nini unasema hivyo?

324
00:18:21,737 --> 00:18:23,605
-Kwa sababu mimi pia
ningefanya jambo lile lile.

325
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:25,409
Kwenye biashara ndogo kama yenu.

326
00:18:25,444 --> 00:18:26,905
Wanajua wanaweza
kuzuia malipo

327
00:18:26,940 --> 00:18:29,215
hadi sekunde ya mwisho kabisa
na kisha kukuangamiza.

328
00:18:29,250 --> 00:18:31,580
Hawa watu, ni...
Ni wanyang'anyi.

329
00:18:31,615 --> 00:18:33,318
-Ndiyo...

330
00:18:35,256 --> 00:18:39,489
-Tumeelewa. Asante.
Eeh...

331
00:18:39,524 --> 00:18:41,458
Unajuaje lolote --

332
00:18:41,493 --> 00:18:44,824
Inanihusu nini mimi?
Una kiasi gani cha pesa?

333
00:18:50,634 --> 00:18:52,766
-Ndiyo, eeh...

334
00:18:52,801 --> 00:18:54,504
-Sawa, jamani?

335
00:18:54,539 --> 00:18:56,605
-Dola mbili na senti hamsini?
-Hivi ndivyo nitakavyofanya.

336
00:18:56,640 --> 00:19:00,213
Nitawapa
dola elfu ishirini taslimu leo.

337
00:19:00,248 --> 00:19:03,249
Nitauza simu, nitatua
tatizo hili na USR.

338
00:19:03,284 --> 00:19:07,781
Lakini nataka asilimia hamsini ya kampuni,
na lazima niwe mkurugenzi mkuu.

339
00:19:12,755 --> 00:19:14,722
-Hiyo ni...
-Unafanya mzaha?

340
00:19:14,757 --> 00:19:17,890
Hapana. Ni dhahiri. Ni dhahiri.
Hapana. Hapana!

341
00:19:17,925 --> 00:19:19,958
-Nipaswa tu --
-Mike?

342
00:19:19,993 --> 00:19:22,796
-Sawa. Sawa.
-Nani anayesimamia hapa?

343
00:19:22,831 --> 00:19:24,732
-Lo, namaanisha, kimsingi --
-Mike ndiye anayesimamia,

344
00:19:24,767 --> 00:19:26,470
na anasema hapana.

345
00:19:32,742 --> 00:19:35,347
-Mimi ndiye ninayesimamia.

346
00:19:35,382 --> 00:19:37,877
Na nasema...

347
00:19:37,912 --> 00:19:39,813
-Samahani.

348
00:19:39,848 --> 00:19:41,650
Huna haja ya kufanya
anachosema mtu huyu.

349
00:19:41,685 --> 00:19:43,289
Tumekutana naye hivi punde.
Yeye si baba yako!

350
00:19:43,324 --> 00:19:44,455
-Sawa...

351
00:19:50,364 --> 00:19:53,629
-Asante. Nakushukuru.

352
00:19:57,800 --> 00:19:59,965
-Mwanaume mwenye kejeli sana.

353
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,406
Hukubaliani nami?

354
00:20:01,441 --> 00:20:05,036
Alikuwa na --
Alikuwa na kejeli.

355
00:20:05,071 --> 00:20:07,313
-"Modemu, ushawahi kuzisikia,"
au chochote kile, kama --

356
00:20:07,348 --> 00:20:10,415
-Ooh, hapana. Nami nilimfanyia kejeli,
lakini alinirudishia kejeli.

357
00:20:12,419 --> 00:20:16,520
Kwani, anajaribu kusema nini?
Kwamba hatuna mkataba wetu wa modemu?

358
00:20:16,555 --> 00:20:19,358
[Anacheka]

359
00:20:19,393 --> 00:20:24,594
[Sauti za michezo ya video,
simu inaita]

360
00:20:24,629 --> 00:20:26,827
<i>-US Robotics.</i>
<i>Nikusaidie kuongea na nani?</i>

361
00:20:26,862 --> 00:20:28,829
-Ndiyo, ni Mike Lazaridis
kutoka Research in Motion.

362
00:20:28,864 --> 00:20:30,699
Kiukweli tunatengeneza
baadhi ya bodi za saketi

363
00:20:30,734 --> 00:20:32,371
kwa ajili yenu.
<i>-Subiri kidogo tafadhali.</i>

364
00:20:32,406 --> 00:20:39,543
[Mlio wa kielektroniki]

365
00:20:39,578 --> 00:20:42,414
<i>-Mike! Ni wewe?</i>
-Ndiyo, habari.

366
00:20:42,449 --> 00:20:46,616
Nilikuwa najiuliza tu kama --
kama ingewezekana --

367
00:20:46,651 --> 00:20:51,016
kama ingewezekana kabisa sisi
kukutumia ankara

368
00:20:51,051 --> 00:20:53,854
kwa nusu ya kwanza au theluthi moja

369
00:20:53,889 --> 00:20:57,495
ya oda -- oda yenu
kutoka kwetu, kama -- kama --

370
00:20:57,530 --> 00:21:01,433
tuna -- tunaweza kukutumia ankara
kwa baadhi ya --

371
00:21:01,468 --> 00:21:05,965
oda yenu.
<i>-[Anacheka] Ooh, nini?</i>

372
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:08,033
<i>Nini?</i>
-Kama ni sawa?

373
00:21:08,068 --> 00:21:10,068
<i>-Je, hukupata faksi yangu?</i>

374
00:21:10,103 --> 00:21:12,774
-Hatuna mashine ya faksi.

375
00:21:12,809 --> 00:21:17,647
<i>-Mike, zile modemu</i>
<i>ulizotutumia mwezi wa Machi,</i>

376
00:21:17,682 --> 00:21:21,453
<i>vilikuwa na kasoro.</i>
-Samahani. Nini?

377
00:21:21,488 --> 00:21:23,653
<i>-Ndiyo, havikufanya kazi.</i>

378
00:21:23,688 --> 00:21:25,391
<i>Tulilazimika kufuta</i>
<i>agizo lote.</i>

379
00:21:25,426 --> 00:21:27,591
<i>Lakini hii ilikuwa miezi iliyopita, rafiki yangu.</i>

380
00:21:29,056 --> 00:21:31,727
<i>Kwa kweli nilidhani ninyi</i>
<i>mnayo mashine ya faksi.</i>

381
00:21:31,762 --> 00:21:34,895
<i>Sikiliza, nakuambia nini, kwa nini</i>
<i>usiniruhusu nikupe fidia?</i>

382
00:21:34,930 --> 00:21:38,096
<i>Nitawafanya USR wakutumie moja</i>
<i>bila gharama yoyote kwa hisani yangu. Sawa?</i>

383
00:21:38,131 --> 00:21:41,539
-Eeh... Ndiyo. Sawa. Ahsante.

384
00:21:41,574 --> 00:21:44,509
<i>-Vyema. Haya basi,</i>
<i>kila la heri, Mike.</i>

385
00:21:44,544 --> 00:21:46,445
-Ndiyo.
<i>-Kwaheri.</i>

386
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:47,512
-Kwaheri.

387
00:21:47,547 --> 00:21:51,450
♪♪

388
00:21:51,485 --> 00:21:55,388
♪♪

389
00:21:55,423 --> 00:21:59,117
♪♪

390
00:21:59,152 --> 00:22:03,055
♪♪

391
00:22:03,090 --> 00:22:06,465
-Nini?

392
00:22:06,500 --> 00:22:09,094
Hiki ndicho unachopaswa kufanya:
Unatakiwa kumpigia simu tena,

393
00:22:09,129 --> 00:22:10,667
lazima
umkomalie vilivyo mtu huyu kama mfanyabiashara shupavu.

394
00:22:10,702 --> 00:22:13,406
Lazima umbane sana.

395
00:22:13,441 --> 00:22:16,101
-Ndiyo...
Sidhani kama ninaweza kumbana.

396
00:22:16,136 --> 00:22:17,707
-Hiki ndicho hasa yule
bwana wa Rolex alisema

397
00:22:17,742 --> 00:22:19,445
kingetokea, sivyo?

398
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:21,073
Alitabiri hilo!
Alisema nini?

399
00:22:21,108 --> 00:22:23,878
Alisema US Robotics ni maharamia.

400
00:22:23,913 --> 00:22:26,144
Alikuwa amepatia hasa.

401
00:22:26,179 --> 00:22:27,981
-Ndiyo.

402
00:22:31,118 --> 00:22:34,625
[Muingiliano wa mawasiliano]
Haya.

403
00:22:36,464 --> 00:22:38,563
-Hujambo, Steve? Steve?
-Naam?

404
00:22:38,598 --> 00:22:40,191
-Nahitaji kutumia simu.

405
00:22:40,226 --> 00:22:44,162
-Kuna mtu anajaribu kusema kwamba
Noonian Soong ni mmoja wa akina Q.

406
00:22:44,197 --> 00:22:45,603
-Shukrani -- ndiyo, asante.

407
00:22:45,638 --> 00:22:47,638
-Haya.
-Unafanya nini?

408
00:22:50,940 --> 00:22:53,974
-Nadhani tunapaswa
kubali makubaliano haya.

409
00:22:54,009 --> 00:22:55,448
-Hapana!

410
00:22:55,483 --> 00:22:56,614
Hapana --

411
00:22:56,649 --> 00:22:58,110
Basi...

412
00:22:58,145 --> 00:23:00,211
Huingii kwenye biashara
na watu wa namna hii.

413
00:23:00,246 --> 00:23:03,181
Yule mtu haaminiki.
-Nadhani yeye ni...

414
00:23:03,216 --> 00:23:05,722
Sidhani kama haaminiki.

415
00:23:05,757 --> 00:23:10,826
-Kadi yake ya biashara
imochorwa tu kwa mkono.

416
00:23:14,194 --> 00:23:16,194
Mtu huyo ni papa.

417
00:23:16,229 --> 00:23:17,899
-Sawa. Je, unajua...

418
00:23:17,934 --> 00:23:20,770
Je, unajua ni nani anawaogopa
papa?

419
00:23:22,774 --> 00:23:24,543
Maharamia.

420
00:23:33,620 --> 00:23:35,983
Ee, basi, hm...

421
00:23:37,690 --> 00:23:42,924
Tumekuwa tukizungumza hapa,
na sisi --

422
00:23:42,959 --> 00:23:45,058
Tungependa kutoa
pendekezo mbadala.

423
00:23:45,093 --> 00:23:48,963
-Mmerudi mkitambaa
kama wadudu, kama mabuu.

424
00:23:48,998 --> 00:23:55,200
-Ndiyo. Hivyo, tungependa
kuwapa...

425
00:23:55,235 --> 00:23:58,940
Asilimia kumi kwa...

426
00:23:58,975 --> 00:24:01,008
Dola laki tano.

427
00:24:01,043 --> 00:24:02,680
-Je, umechanganyikiwa kabisa?!

428
00:24:02,715 --> 00:24:04,550
Nakagua fursa laki moja kila siku!

429
00:24:04,585 --> 00:24:06,244
Nachagua moja!
Hivyo ndivyo nukuu inavyosema?

430
00:24:06,279 --> 00:24:10,721
Hapana. Nakagua fursa mia moja kila siku!
Nachagua moja! "Wall Street."

431
00:24:10,756 --> 00:24:15,759
-Sawa, eeh, k--
eeh...

432
00:24:15,794 --> 00:24:18,564
Asilimia 25 kwa dola laki mbili na nusu.

433
00:24:18,599 --> 00:24:20,731
-Asilimia 50 kwa dola hamsini!

434
00:24:20,766 --> 00:24:24,295
-Asilimia 33 kwa dola laki moja na elfu ishirini na tano,

435
00:24:24,330 --> 00:24:27,573
na unaweza kuongoza kampuni pamoja nami.

436
00:24:27,608 --> 00:24:31,170
-Mike? Hapana! Hapana!
Ndiyo. Tumekubaliana. Tumekubaliana.

437
00:24:31,205 --> 00:24:34,008
-Sawa.
-Tulia. Rafiki.

438
00:24:37,948 --> 00:24:40,685
Kila kitu kitakuwa sawa kabisa.

439
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:44,623
Utamzidi ujanja mtu huyu kwenye majadiliano mpaka akose la kusema.

440
00:24:46,088 --> 00:24:54,567
[Matangazo ya hoki kwenye televisheni]

441
00:24:54,602 --> 00:24:56,701
<i>-Goli!</i>

442
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:04,269
[Simu inaita]

443
00:25:04,304 --> 00:25:05,809
-Ndiyo?
-Habari, Jim.

444
00:25:05,844 --> 00:25:08,713
Ni Mike Lazaridis kutoka Research in Motion.

445
00:25:08,748 --> 00:25:11,012
Tulikutana ofisini siku chache zilizopita.

446
00:25:19,660 --> 00:25:23,596
Hivyo basi, tungependa kukupa...

447
00:25:23,631 --> 00:25:27,259
Asilimia 33 ya kampuni yetu kwa dola laki moja na elfu ishirini na tano,

448
00:25:27,294 --> 00:25:31,131
na mimi na wewe tutakuwa wakurugenzi wakuu wenza.

449
00:25:33,707 --> 00:25:35,773
<i>-...kipindi.</i>
<i>Baadhi yao wanatiliwa shaka.</i>

450
00:25:35,808 --> 00:25:38,336
<i>Huo ni mkwaju wao wa nane katika mchezo huu wa hoki ndani ya dakika 6:44.</i>

451
00:25:38,371 --> 00:25:40,712
-Hakika.
<i>-Hayo ni maendeleo.</i>

452
00:25:50,284 --> 00:25:52,086
-Tumekubaliana.

453
00:25:55,223 --> 00:25:58,092
-Safi sana!
Aisee! Rafiki!

454
00:25:58,127 --> 00:26:02,327
Mike! Scott! Scott?
Amefanikiwa!

455
00:26:02,362 --> 00:26:03,999
-Unamaanisha nini?

456
00:26:04,034 --> 00:26:05,737
-Kwani hukusikia chochote
kilichokuwa kikiendelea

457
00:26:05,772 --> 00:26:07,838
ndani ya chumba hiki?

458
00:26:07,873 --> 00:26:13,646
♪♪

459
00:26:13,681 --> 00:26:19,245
♪♪

460
00:26:19,280 --> 00:26:25,020
♪♪

461
00:26:25,055 --> 00:26:30,828
♪♪

462
00:26:30,863 --> 00:26:32,291
-Unaweza kupata,
kama dakika mbili hivi

463
00:26:32,326 --> 00:26:35,030
-Labda unapaswa kuwaambia
kuhusu vifaa vya mtandao.

464
00:26:39,003 --> 00:26:43,038
-Laiti, unataka
umweke wapi?

465
00:26:45,207 --> 00:26:48,340
-Huu ni upuuzi gani huu?

466
00:26:48,375 --> 00:26:50,342
-Hiyo ni -- ndiyo,
kila mtu anajenga meza yake mwenyewe.

467
00:26:50,377 --> 00:26:53,851
Hiyo -- hiyo ni mila.
-Sawa, mimi sifanyi hivyo.

468
00:26:53,886 --> 00:26:57,756
-Kampuni ya US Robotics imejitoa
kwenye makubaliano.

469
00:26:57,791 --> 00:27:00,055
-Nilikuambia.
Tumewekeza kiasi gani katika hatari?

470
00:27:00,090 --> 00:27:02,794
-Hatari ya hasara?
-Ni kiasi gani cha fedha

471
00:27:02,829 --> 00:27:04,191
ulichotumia kwenye vifaa vya mtandao?

472
00:27:04,226 --> 00:27:06,732
-Dola milioni moja nukta sita.

473
00:27:06,767 --> 00:27:10,032
-Moja nukta nini?!
-Nini?!

474
00:27:10,067 --> 00:27:12,837
-Tulitumia dola milioni moja nukta sita
kwa vifaa na nguvu kazi.

475
00:27:12,872 --> 00:27:16,203
-Ulipata wapi dola milioni moja nukta sita?

476
00:27:16,238 --> 00:27:19,107
-Nilipata mkopo
kutoka Benki ya Montreal.

477
00:27:19,142 --> 00:27:20,878
-Mike, tafadhali.

478
00:27:20,913 --> 00:27:23,111
-Nitafutie US Robotics!

479
00:27:28,756 --> 00:27:30,481
-S-- Samahani,
unazungumza na nani?

480
00:27:30,516 --> 00:27:32,791
-Ndiyo.

481
00:27:32,826 --> 00:27:34,925
[Modemu inalia]
-Hicho ni kitu gani sasa?

482
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:39,193
-Ah, inaitwa wimbi la mawasiliano.
Modemu inayopiga ni --

483
00:27:44,299 --> 00:27:48,334
-Hebu! Ondoka
kwenye hiyo Intaneti!

484
00:27:53,473 --> 00:27:56,045
-Ndiyo.
-Mike?

485
00:27:56,080 --> 00:28:00,478
-Nadhani ni Casey.
-A-haa.

486
00:28:00,513 --> 00:28:05,054
-Mambo yatakuwa sawa, hapana,
yatakuwa sawa.

487
00:28:05,089 --> 00:28:07,958
[Simu inaita]

488
00:28:07,993 --> 00:28:09,927
Huruhusiwi kuzungumza
na timu yetu namna hiyo.

489
00:28:09,962 --> 00:28:11,797
Unaruhusiwa tu kuzungumza -
<i>-Mike!</i>

490
00:28:11,832 --> 00:28:14,129
-Habari. Kwa kweli, hapana.
Huyu ni Jim Balsillie.

491
00:28:14,164 --> 00:28:16,329
Mimi ndiye Mkurugenzi Mkuu hapa sasa.
-Mkurugenzi Mkuu Mwenza.

492
00:28:16,364 --> 00:28:18,969
<i>-Sawa, Jim,</i>
<i>nikusaidie nini?</i>

493
00:28:19,004 --> 00:28:21,202
-Nataka tuzungumze
kuhusu hizi modemu.

494
00:28:21,237 --> 00:28:23,842
<i>-Basi, hakuna cha</i>
<i>kuzungumzia, kwa bahati mbaya --</i>

495
00:28:23,877 --> 00:28:26,042
<i>h-hatuwezi kupokea</i>
<i>bidhaa yenye kasoro.</i>

496
00:28:26,077 --> 00:28:29,210
-Tuache maneno yasiyo na maana hapa.
Dola milioni mbili na nusu, kwa zote,

497
00:28:29,245 --> 00:28:31,916
kwa oda nzima.
<i>-Ndiyo. Hapana, haiwezekani, Jim.</i>

498
00:28:31,951 --> 00:28:34,215
-Basi nitaishusha bei vibaya mno kwako.
Dola milioni moja nukta sita.

499
00:28:34,250 --> 00:28:37,152
Na kama hutaichukua hiyo,
nitageuka na kuwauzia

500
00:28:37,187 --> 00:28:39,858
Rockwell kwa bei ya chini hata zaidi.

501
00:28:39,893 --> 00:28:41,420
-Hayo ndiyo majadiliano.

502
00:28:41,455 --> 00:28:44,126
<i>-Sawa, vipi kuhusu hili?</i>
<i>Tutachukua modemu hizo</i>

503
00:28:44,161 --> 00:28:47,096
<i>ikiwa utaongeza hati miliki</i>
<i>ya simu ya Mike.</i>

504
00:28:51,399 --> 00:28:53,465
-Simu gani?

505
00:28:53,500 --> 00:28:55,973
<i>-Nilidhani hatukuwa</i>
<i>tunadanganyana, Jim.</i>

506
00:28:56,008 --> 00:28:59,141
<i>Tumekuwa tukitengeneza yetu wenyewe</i>
kwa mwaka sasa, tunataka M--

507
00:28:59,176 --> 00:29:01,110
-Inachukua muda gani kutengeneza kielelezo
cha simu hiyo?

508
00:29:01,145 --> 00:29:05,048
-Ile Pocket Link?
Ndiyo -- mwaka mmoja.

509
00:29:05,083 --> 00:29:07,248
-Hapana, hapana, hapana.
Kielelezo cha awali, Mike.

510
00:29:07,283 --> 00:29:08,986
Ganda tu
ambalo naweza kuonyesha kwenye mkutano.

511
00:29:09,021 --> 00:29:10,515
Inaweza kuwa
kitu kisichofanya kazi kabisa.

512
00:29:10,550 --> 00:29:12,583
-Hapana, hiyo --
hatufanyi hivyo.

513
00:29:12,618 --> 00:29:14,992
-Hapana, sisi...
Mike hafanyi hivyo.

514
00:29:15,027 --> 00:29:17,357
-N-nisikilize: US Robotics
wanatengeneza simu yao wenyewe.

515
00:29:17,392 --> 00:29:19,425
Sasa tupo kwenye mbio
za kuingiza kitu hiki sokoni,

516
00:29:19,460 --> 00:29:20,899
na tuko nyuma kwa mwaka mmoja.

517
00:29:20,934 --> 00:29:22,263
Hivyo sijali
unachohitaji kufanya.

518
00:29:22,298 --> 00:29:24,298
Wafanye hawa wataalamu
waache kila kitu

519
00:29:24,333 --> 00:29:27,004
na watengeneze simu hii mara moja!

520
00:29:27,039 --> 00:29:29,237
Nini?!

521
00:29:29,272 --> 00:29:32,141
-Samahani, jamani, um...

522
00:29:32,176 --> 00:29:34,407
Mpenzi wangu alijaribu kuchukua pesa za
hundi yangu leo asubuhi

523
00:29:34,442 --> 00:29:37,344
na ikakataliwa, na akasema

524
00:29:37,379 --> 00:29:39,181
Sipaswi
kuja hapa -- kuruhusiwa --

525
00:29:39,216 --> 00:29:40,886
Sipaswi kuja
hapa tena.

526
00:29:40,921 --> 00:29:44,285
Naye akakubali, sitakuwa nikija hapa tena

527
00:29:44,320 --> 00:29:47,321
mpaka nitakapoanza kulipwa.
-Aisee!

528
00:29:50,392 --> 00:29:54,493
-[Anashusha pumzi]

529
00:29:54,528 --> 00:29:56,330
Ninaweza kurekebisha hili.

530
00:30:03,636 --> 00:30:05,603
-Sawa, Research in Motion.

531
00:30:05,638 --> 00:30:10,443
Inaonekana akaunti yako imezidi kiwango chake cha mkopo.

532
00:30:10,478 --> 00:30:14,315
-Je, hawakuweka hundi ya dola 125,000 kutoka kwangu hivi punde?

533
00:30:16,319 --> 00:30:18,121
-Ndiyo.

534
00:30:23,095 --> 00:30:25,865
-Sawa. Vizuri.
Eeh...

535
00:30:29,167 --> 00:30:33,598
Nina mkopo wa nyumba kwenu.
Tunaweza kuuangalia huo, tafadhali?

536
00:30:33,633 --> 00:30:35,974
-Tahaji jina lako la ukoo, tafadhali.

537
00:30:36,009 --> 00:30:39,472
-B-A-L-S-I-L-L-I-E.

538
00:30:39,507 --> 00:30:43,542
-"Ball-SILLY"?
-"BAHLS-lee"

539
00:30:43,577 --> 00:30:46,611
-Kuna mtu atakayekikosa kiti hiki chekundu?

540
00:30:46,646 --> 00:30:48,646
-Hapana.
-Ni sawa.

541
00:30:48,681 --> 00:30:52,056
-Watu tofauti,
kifaa tofauti.

542
00:30:52,091 --> 00:30:54,960
[Mlango unafunguka]

543
00:30:54,995 --> 00:30:57,193
-Haya, kila mmoja,
nisikilizeni.

544
00:30:57,228 --> 00:30:59,360
Kuanzia sasa, hundi zitakuwa zinatolewa kila baada ya wiki mbili.

545
00:30:59,395 --> 00:31:01,131
Mtakuja kuzichukua kwa Shelly.

546
00:31:01,166 --> 00:31:03,265
Huyu ndiye Shelly.
-Habari.

547
00:31:13,244 --> 00:31:15,343
-Haya.
Huyo ni wewe, Shell.

548
00:31:17,512 --> 00:31:19,281
Mike!

549
00:31:22,022 --> 00:31:23,989
-Mimi pia?
-Ndiyo, bila shaka.

550
00:31:32,725 --> 00:31:35,429
-Samahani. Ni nani --
Kwani, huyu Shelly ni nani?

551
00:31:35,464 --> 00:31:37,134
[Mlio wa mawasiliano]
-Shelly?

552
00:31:37,169 --> 00:31:40,137
-Ala, ndugu,
kitu hicho kinakuandama.

553
00:31:40,172 --> 00:31:41,600
-Hapana, ninakupa hamasa.

554
00:31:41,635 --> 00:31:44,240
Na usiniite kitu hicho.
Mimi ni bosi wako.

555
00:31:44,275 --> 00:31:46,077
-Hapana. Hapana, wewe siye.
-Ati?

556
00:31:46,112 --> 00:31:47,540
-Nitafutie John Woodman
huko Bell Atlantic.

557
00:31:47,575 --> 00:31:50,642
-Sawa kabisa.
-Subiri, unafanya nini?

558
00:31:50,677 --> 00:31:54,712
-Tunauza simu hii.
Mike, nahitaji kielelezo cha awali.

559
00:31:54,747 --> 00:31:56,483
-Nilikuambia, mimi sina --
-Mike?

560
00:31:56,518 --> 00:31:58,254
[Mlio]
<i>-Tunakuunganisha.</i>

561
00:31:58,289 --> 00:32:02,126
-Jamani, tuna deni la zaidi ya dola milioni moja
bila rasilimali yoyote,

562
00:32:02,161 --> 00:32:04,997
bila mikataba wala bidhaa.

563
00:32:05,032 --> 00:32:07,329
<i>-Ofisi ya John Woodman.</i>
-Habari, hapa ni Jim Balsillie,

564
00:32:07,364 --> 00:32:10,167
Mkurugenzi Mkuu wa Research in Motion.
-Mkurugenzi Mshiriki.

565
00:32:10,202 --> 00:32:12,697
<i>-Subiri kidogo, tafadhali.</i>
-[Anatamka kwa midomo tu]

566
00:32:12,732 --> 00:32:15,172
Sawa?
-Ndiyo, mimi --

567
00:32:15,207 --> 00:32:18,340
-Hapana! Amesema hakuna simu!
-Sikuulizi wewe!

568
00:32:20,443 --> 00:32:23,444
Mike.

569
00:32:23,479 --> 00:32:24,775
-Sawa.
-“Sawa” --

570
00:32:24,810 --> 00:32:26,612
unamaanisha nini, sawa?

571
00:32:26,647 --> 00:32:28,581
Hapana, hapana, subiri. Subiri kidogo.
Subiri kidogo. Subiri kidogo.

572
00:32:28,616 --> 00:32:30,616
Subiri, subiri, subiri kidogo.
Subiri kidogo.

573
00:32:30,651 --> 00:32:32,618
<i>-John Whitman.</i>
-Bwana Woodman, ninakaribia

574
00:32:32,653 --> 00:32:34,455
kukufanya uwe tajiri wa kupindukia.

575
00:32:34,490 --> 00:32:37,293
[Mlio wa kukata]

576
00:32:41,365 --> 00:32:44,564
-Mike hakubaliani na hili?
-Amekubali sasa hivi!

577
00:32:44,599 --> 00:32:47,468
-Hayo yalikuwa ni mashinikizo! Sawa?!
Unamchezea akili!

578
00:32:47,503 --> 00:32:50,702
Iko wazi!
Unataka nifanye nini?

579
00:32:50,737 --> 00:32:52,209
-Eeh...
-Nini?

580
00:32:52,244 --> 00:32:56,642
[Mvumo wa chini]

581
00:32:56,677 --> 00:32:59,810
-Hivyo kuna sababu
kwa nini simu yako ya ndani

582
00:32:59,845 --> 00:33:01,647
inatoa sauti ya mparuzano.

583
00:33:01,682 --> 00:33:04,419
Ni kwa sababu ilitengenezwa China

584
00:33:04,454 --> 00:33:07,092
na wahandisi ambao hawakujali.

585
00:33:07,127 --> 00:33:09,622
Na sasa kila ofisi
duniani

586
00:33:09,657 --> 00:33:12,328
inalazimika kuvumilia mparuzano unaokera,

587
00:33:12,363 --> 00:33:16,497
taa nyekundu inayowaka na kuzima,
kamba kumi na tano tofauti za umeme

588
00:33:16,532 --> 00:33:18,730
ambazo hazioani kabisa
moja na nyingine.

589
00:33:18,765 --> 00:33:21,370
Hivyo basi hatufanyi hivyo.

590
00:33:21,405 --> 00:33:25,308
Hatuongezi tu
mparuzano huo.

591
00:33:25,343 --> 00:33:27,475
Nitatengeneza kielelezo cha awali,

592
00:33:27,510 --> 00:33:31,677
lakini nitakifanya kwa ukamilifu
au nisikifanye kabisa.

593
00:33:31,712 --> 00:33:33,811
-Mike, unajua ule msemo

594
00:33:33,846 --> 00:33:35,813
"ukamilifu ni adui wa uzuri"?

595
00:33:35,848 --> 00:33:40,488
♪♪

596
00:33:40,523 --> 00:33:44,525
-Basi, bora tu
ni adui wa ubinadamu.

597
00:34:05,449 --> 00:34:07,416
-[Anashusha pumzi]

598
00:34:15,195 --> 00:34:18,493
Shelley, niunganishe tena na
John Woodman, tafadhali.

599
00:34:18,528 --> 00:34:21,760
-Hivyo nikanyoosha mkono,
nikakata simu.

600
00:34:21,795 --> 00:34:24,466
Alinitazama kama kusema,
"Je, uko tayari kufa?"

601
00:34:24,501 --> 00:34:26,402
-[Anacheka]
-Hapana, hapana, hapana, hapana.

602
00:34:26,437 --> 00:34:28,239
Na niko tayari kufa kwa ajili ya hilo.

603
00:34:28,274 --> 00:34:32,144
Sivyo?
Mike anaingia katikati yetu,

604
00:34:32,179 --> 00:34:34,674
anashusha miwani chini
na kusema,

605
00:34:34,709 --> 00:34:38,810
"Wewe, nitakuambia lini tutapanga
ule mkutano."

606
00:34:38,845 --> 00:34:40,350
Naye anarudi nyuma.

607
00:34:40,385 --> 00:34:42,286
-Ooh!
-Sawa kabisa!

608
00:34:42,321 --> 00:34:43,584
Woodman anataka kukiona.

609
00:34:43,619 --> 00:34:45,454
Tunakwenda
Bell Atlantic kesho.

610
00:34:45,489 --> 00:34:48,886
-Subiri, nini?
-Jiji la New York kesho.

611
00:34:48,921 --> 00:34:51,361
-Lakini alisema --
-Una muda mpaka saa mbili asubuhi.

612
00:34:51,396 --> 00:34:52,758
-K-kufanya nini?

613
00:34:55,433 --> 00:34:56,795
-Kwa hiyo, hukumwita hivyo, au siyo?

614
00:34:56,830 --> 00:34:58,632
-Sawa. Sawa.

615
00:35:01,538 --> 00:35:03,571
Haya, mpango mpya, kila mmoja.

616
00:35:03,606 --> 00:35:06,838
Sote tutachangia nguvu
na kuunda kifaa hiki usiku wa leo.

617
00:35:06,873 --> 00:35:08,576
Sawa?

618
00:35:08,611 --> 00:35:13,317
♪♪

619
00:35:13,352 --> 00:35:15,220
-Haya, nipe
swichi ya kugeuzia ya Fillmore.

620
00:35:15,255 --> 00:35:17,189
Nipe 33PF, ee...
-Ndiyo.

621
00:35:17,224 --> 00:35:19,818
-Nadhani ni kama
kitu fulani cha

622
00:35:19,853 --> 00:35:21,655
aina ya mchanganyiko.
Hivyo napenda ile...

623
00:35:21,690 --> 00:35:23,195
-Nilidhani ulikuwa unacheza
"Civ."

624
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:24,790
-Tumerudi.

625
00:35:27,663 --> 00:35:29,729
-Nina kitu kwa ajili yako.

626
00:35:29,764 --> 00:35:36,208
♪♪

627
00:35:36,243 --> 00:35:42,478
♪♪

628
00:35:42,513 --> 00:35:45,316
-Ndiyo maana kwangu mimi,
yaani, vidhibiti mbali...

629
00:35:47,287 --> 00:35:49,353
-Vitufe ni vidogo kiasi kwamba...

630
00:35:49,388 --> 00:35:56,327
♪♪

631
00:35:56,362 --> 00:35:58,692
-Kuna miiba ya neva,
mawasiliano yamepotea.

632
00:35:58,727 --> 00:36:00,463
-Unakivua?
-Ndiyo.

633
00:36:00,498 --> 00:36:02,795
Tutaonana kesho, jamani.
-Ndiyo.

634
00:36:02,830 --> 00:36:06,601
-Hivyo kuongeza ayoni ya lithiamu
kunafanya nini...

635
00:36:06,636 --> 00:36:14,312
♪♪

636
00:36:14,347 --> 00:36:16,380
-Bado ni moto. Bado ni moto.

637
00:36:16,415 --> 00:36:18,382
♪♪

638
00:36:18,417 --> 00:36:20,813
[Kukoroma, mlango unafunguka]

639
00:36:24,588 --> 00:36:26,687
[Honi inalia]

640
00:36:26,722 --> 00:36:29,558
-[Anaguna]
Niliota kwamba tulikuwa matajiri.

641
00:36:29,593 --> 00:36:32,297
[Mshindo wa vyombo]

642
00:36:32,332 --> 00:36:39,634
[Honi inayolia mfululizo]

643
00:36:46,742 --> 00:36:51,008
Na wakati mwingine ndoto zangu hutokea
sawia na vile nilivyoota.

644
00:36:51,043 --> 00:36:53,043
-Twende!

645
00:36:53,078 --> 00:36:56,849
-Hiyo imetoka wapi?

646
00:36:56,884 --> 00:36:58,587
-"Dune."

647
00:36:58,622 --> 00:37:03,493
♪♪

648
00:37:03,528 --> 00:37:08,432
♪♪

649
00:37:08,467 --> 00:37:13,338
♪♪

650
00:37:13,373 --> 00:37:14,900
-A-haa!

651
00:37:14,935 --> 00:37:16,473
-Utavaa
uko uwanja wa ndege.

652
00:37:16,508 --> 00:37:18,442
-Ndiyo. Asante.

653
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:23,711
-Je, Doug aje nasi au--

654
00:37:23,746 --> 00:37:25,482
-Hapana.

655
00:37:25,517 --> 00:37:28,518
-Kwa sababu anahusika sana
na jambo hili.

656
00:37:28,553 --> 00:37:32,016
-Yeye ni wa mzaha tu.
Ingia kwenye gari.

657
00:37:32,051 --> 00:37:35,921
-Ndiyo, nadhani
anataka sana kuja.

658
00:37:35,956 --> 00:37:38,627
-Ngoja nikuambie ushauri bora
zaidi niliowahi kupata kule Harvard.

659
00:37:38,662 --> 00:37:40,959
Ukitaka kuwa mkuu,
unapaswa kujitoa mhanga.

660
00:37:40,994 --> 00:37:45,634
Kadiri unavyojitoa kwa maumivu,
ndivyo utakavyokuwa mkuu zaidi.

661
00:37:48,936 --> 00:37:50,771
-Yeye -- ni rafiki yangu wa dhati.

662
00:37:50,806 --> 00:37:54,379
-Sawa, vyema. Nilimwona akiweka
kizibua choo juu ya kompyuta.

663
00:37:54,414 --> 00:37:56,777
[Anashusha pumzi]

664
00:37:56,812 --> 00:38:04,389
♪♪

665
00:38:04,424 --> 00:38:11,792
♪♪

666
00:38:11,827 --> 00:38:15,730
<i>-Abiria wa ndege</i>
<i>namba AC42 kuelekea New York,</i>

667
00:38:15,765 --> 00:38:17,930
<i>mnaanza kuingia</i>
<i>ndani ya ndege sasa.</i>

668
00:38:17,965 --> 00:38:25,773
♪♪

669
00:38:25,808 --> 00:38:33,616
♪♪

670
00:38:33,651 --> 00:38:37,422
-♪ Sauti ililia kwa upole ♪

671
00:38:37,457 --> 00:38:40,590
♪ Nje ya dirisha ♪

672
00:38:40,625 --> 00:38:46,464
♪♪

673
00:38:46,499 --> 00:38:52,096
♪♪

674
00:38:52,131 --> 00:38:54,065
[Muziki unaendelea kwenye redio,
kelele za magari]

675
00:38:54,100 --> 00:38:55,704
♪♪

676
00:38:55,739 --> 00:38:58,971
[Anatafuna kwa sauti]

677
00:38:59,006 --> 00:39:03,976
♪♪

678
00:39:04,011 --> 00:39:06,913
-Hebu, acha mambo hayo.

679
00:39:06,948 --> 00:39:09,454
Kwa hiyo, ukinisikia
nikikunjakunja karatasi,

680
00:39:09,489 --> 00:39:11,786
hiyo inamaanisha uache kuongea.

681
00:39:13,955 --> 00:39:16,120
-Inamaanisha kwa ujumla au...

682
00:39:16,155 --> 00:39:18,991
-Hapana, kwenye -- [anashusha pumzi]
Kwenye uwasilishaji.

683
00:39:19,026 --> 00:39:21,026
-Sawa. Nimekuelewa.

684
00:39:24,196 --> 00:39:26,999
-Haya, tunapaswa kuondoka hapa, bwana!
Mke wangu ana uchungu wa uzazi!

685
00:39:27,034 --> 00:39:28,473
Twende!

686
00:39:28,508 --> 00:39:35,139
♪♪

687
00:39:35,174 --> 00:39:37,614
-Naweza -- naweza kuuliza kwa nini
kadi yako ya biashara

688
00:39:37,649 --> 00:39:39,583
ilikuwa imefutwa namba ya simu?

689
00:39:41,686 --> 00:39:43,917
-Sijui kabisa
unachokizungumzia.

690
00:39:47,153 --> 00:39:48,790
-Hebu tufanye makubaliano, sawa?

691
00:39:48,825 --> 00:39:50,990
Mimi na wewe tusiwe tunadanganyana.

692
00:39:58,901 --> 00:40:01,605
-Sawa.

693
00:40:01,640 --> 00:40:03,035
Sikuacha kazi yangu.

694
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:05,543
Nilifutwa kazi.

695
00:40:05,578 --> 00:40:08,172
Na nimeiweka nyumba yangu rehani
ili kuwalipa wafanyakazi wetu.

696
00:40:08,207 --> 00:40:11,846
Kwa hiyo, hili lisipofanikiwa,
nimekwisha.

697
00:40:15,819 --> 00:40:19,051
-Kwa nini walikufuta kazi?

698
00:40:19,086 --> 00:40:20,756
-Kwa sababu ni wajinga.

699
00:40:35,234 --> 00:40:37,069
[Kengele ya lifti inalia]

700
00:40:45,552 --> 00:40:47,277
-Habari! Research in Motion?
-U hali gani?

701
00:40:47,312 --> 00:40:49,081
-Safi sana.
Je, nikuletee chochote?

702
00:40:49,116 --> 00:40:50,918
Kahawa? Maji?
-Tuko sawa. Tuko sawa.

703
00:40:50,953 --> 00:40:53,723
-Sawa.
Watakuja kuwaona hivi punde.

704
00:40:53,758 --> 00:40:55,791
-Sawa. Asante. Vyema.
-Vizuri.

705
00:40:59,830 --> 00:41:01,731
-Jim?
-Hapana, hapana, hapana, hapana.

706
00:41:01,766 --> 00:41:03,293
Kamwe usipokee vinywaji.

707
00:41:03,328 --> 00:41:05,163
Kiu ni ishara ya udhaifu.

708
00:41:05,198 --> 00:41:07,803
-Hapana, huenda nimesahau simu.

709
00:41:10,577 --> 00:41:13,578
-Tafadhali niambie unatania.
-Hapana, ninasema kweli kabisa.

710
00:41:13,613 --> 00:41:15,613
-Lahaula!

711
00:41:20,884 --> 00:41:22,785
-Sawa,
hiki ndicho tutakachofanya.

712
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:24,281
Nahitaji uchore
mchoro mdogo.

713
00:41:24,316 --> 00:41:25,887
-Sawa.
-Sawa? Kitu kinachoonesha

714
00:41:25,922 --> 00:41:26,987
kibodi
kama ulivyofanya ofisini kwangu.

715
00:41:27,022 --> 00:41:28,824
-Sawa. Ndiyo. Sawa.

716
00:41:28,859 --> 00:41:30,694
-Samahani, binti.
Naweza kukuomba

717
00:41:30,729 --> 00:41:32,597
kalamu na karatasi, tafadhali?

718
00:41:32,632 --> 00:41:38,735
♪♪

719
00:41:38,770 --> 00:41:40,737
-Wako tayari kwa ajili yenu.

720
00:41:43,643 --> 00:41:45,137
-Vyema.

721
00:41:45,172 --> 00:41:49,713
♪♪

722
00:41:49,748 --> 00:41:51,143
-Ndiyo. Ndiyo, ni sahihi.

723
00:41:51,178 --> 00:41:52,584
Lo, subiri, subiri. Huyu hapa.

724
00:41:52,619 --> 00:41:54,784
-Usijali, sawa.
-Habari.

725
00:41:54,819 --> 00:41:55,983
-Habari.
-Habari.

726
00:41:56,018 --> 00:41:58,315
-Habari yako?
-Nzuri.

727
00:41:58,350 --> 00:42:00,988
Vema. Je, tunasubiri mtu mwingine yeyote?

728
00:42:05,027 --> 00:42:06,829
-Niko peke yangu.

729
00:42:10,065 --> 00:42:11,834
-Sawa.

730
00:42:15,675 --> 00:42:19,743
-Vema. Haya basi, wenzangu.

731
00:42:19,778 --> 00:42:21,371
Hivi ndivyo ninavyoliona suala hili.

732
00:42:21,406 --> 00:42:23,615
Haya, sasa, najua timu yenu ya masoko

733
00:42:23,650 --> 00:42:25,980
inawaambia kuwa mnauza umoja,

734
00:42:26,015 --> 00:42:28,719
familia au kudumisha mawasiliano na kadhalika,

735
00:42:28,754 --> 00:42:31,623
lakini tuwe waaminifu:

736
00:42:31,658 --> 00:42:34,285
mnauza dakika, nukta.

737
00:42:34,320 --> 00:42:38,058
Namaanisha, soko lenu ni dakika,

738
00:42:38,093 --> 00:42:40,830
hivyo mshindani wenu mkuu si kampuni nyingine za simu za mkononi,

739
00:42:40,865 --> 00:42:43,228
ni simu za nyumbani na za ofisini.

740
00:42:43,263 --> 00:42:47,771
Hizo ni dakika za bure. Hizo ni dakika zinazopotea.

741
00:42:47,806 --> 00:42:52,875
Hivyo, tunazirudishaje dakika hizo?

742
00:42:52,910 --> 00:42:54,877
Tunaitengeneza upya simu ya mkononi.

743
00:42:54,912 --> 00:42:57,176
Tunaweka kompyuta ndani yake. Tunaweka intaneti ndani yake.

744
00:42:57,211 --> 00:43:00,949
Tunafanya simu yako ya mkononi kuwa na manufaa makubwa mno

745
00:43:00,984 --> 00:43:03,347
kiasi kwamba hutahitaji tena kwenda ofisini.

746
00:43:03,382 --> 00:43:06,691
Inashughulikia barua pepe, ujumbe mfupi, namna yoyote unayotaka kuwasiliana;

747
00:43:06,726 --> 00:43:10,354
uhuru kamili wa mtu binafsi vyote katika kifaa kimoja --

748
00:43:10,389 --> 00:43:13,797
kinachotoshea kiganjani mwako.

749
00:43:13,832 --> 00:43:16,701
Hivyo, unaweza kuiambia timu yako ya masoko

750
00:43:16,736 --> 00:43:20,364
kuwa hamuuzi tena umoja.

751
00:43:20,399 --> 00:43:23,103
Unauza ujitegemeaji.

752
00:43:27,175 --> 00:43:29,846
-Ee...

753
00:43:29,881 --> 00:43:34,279
Wewe si mtaalamu wa teknolojia,
sivyo?

754
00:43:34,314 --> 00:43:37,084
-Mimi si --

755
00:43:37,119 --> 00:43:39,856
-Dunia nzima...

756
00:43:39,891 --> 00:43:41,858
Dunia nzima hii kabisa

757
00:43:41,893 --> 00:43:43,893
inajaribu kutumia barua pepe
kwenye simu ya mkononi.

758
00:43:43,928 --> 00:43:45,862
Tulikuwa na idara nzima
ikiifanyia kazi kwa,

759
00:43:45,897 --> 00:43:47,732
sijui,
takriban miezi minane hivi.

760
00:43:47,767 --> 00:43:51,296
Unajua ni simu ngapi walizoweza kuzifanya
zifanye kazi kwa wakati mmoja?

761
00:43:53,432 --> 00:43:55,201
Kumi na moja.

762
00:43:57,073 --> 00:43:59,436
Namaanisha, ni mtandao
uliotengenezwa kwa ajili ya vifaa vya ujumbe.

763
00:43:59,471 --> 00:44:01,273
Hicho ndicho tu unachoweza kufanya.

764
00:44:01,308 --> 00:44:04,012
Uko ndotoni tu kwenye --
[anacheka] kwenye hili, unajua,

765
00:44:04,047 --> 00:44:08,984
una -- Nadhani, unajua,
kuna wataalamu wamekupotosha.

766
00:44:12,484 --> 00:44:14,286
-Sawa.

767
00:44:18,798 --> 00:44:21,392
Mike?
-Nini kimetokea?

768
00:44:21,427 --> 00:44:23,262
-Haitafanya kazi.
-Unamaanisha nini kusema haitafanya kazi?

769
00:44:23,297 --> 00:44:26,067
-Mike? Wameshaijaribu tayari.
-Mmeijaribuje hii tayari?

770
00:44:26,102 --> 00:44:27,871
-Jamani, nadhani
mkutano umeisha.

771
00:44:27,906 --> 00:44:30,368
-Je, mliweka vifaa vyenu
moja kwa moja kwenye mtandao

772
00:44:30,403 --> 00:44:34,108
kana kwamba vilikuwa vifaa pokezi?

773
00:44:34,143 --> 00:44:35,472
-Ndiyo, ni sawa.
-Naam, kweli.

774
00:44:35,507 --> 00:44:37,881
Hivyo hiyo iliwasaidia nini?
Kama, simu kumi zikifanya kazi

775
00:44:37,916 --> 00:44:43,348
kwa wakati mmoja?

776
00:44:43,383 --> 00:44:45,922
-Ee, naam.
-Haya, hapa,

777
00:44:45,957 --> 00:44:48,793
nishikie hapa kwa sekunde moja.
Haya, hili ndilo tatizo lenu.

778
00:44:48,828 --> 00:44:52,324
Unapo--unapotumia simu
kama kifaampokezi, inakuwa inafanya nini?

779
00:44:52,359 --> 00:44:55,998
Inakaa tu kwenye mtandao wenu
ikiuliza mfululizo

780
00:44:56,033 --> 00:44:58,803
swali lilelile:
Je, nimepata barua pepe?

781
00:44:58,838 --> 00:45:00,134
Je, nimepata barua pepe?
Je, nimepata barua pepe?

782
00:45:00,169 --> 00:45:03,434
Hivyo inavuta data kila wakati
kwenye seva zenu

783
00:45:03,469 --> 00:45:05,843
iwe umepata barua pepe au la.

784
00:45:05,878 --> 00:45:07,944
Tuna suluhisho.
Sawa?

785
00:45:07,979 --> 00:45:12,113
Hivyo basi, tutatengeneza
kompyuta kubwa

786
00:45:12,148 --> 00:45:15,017
itakayofanya kazi kama
kifaampokezi kikubwa

787
00:45:15,052 --> 00:45:17,349
ambayo imeunganishwa moja kwa moja
kwenye intaneti kwa waya

788
00:45:17,384 --> 00:45:21,958
huku simu yetu ikiwa kama seva.

789
00:45:21,993 --> 00:45:24,389
Haya, hivyo mtumiaji
anapopata barua pepe,

790
00:45:24,424 --> 00:45:28,129
Waterloo inaivuta,
inaifunga vyema,

791
00:45:28,164 --> 00:45:32,100
na kisha...

792
00:45:32,135 --> 00:45:35,004
inaituma.

793
00:45:35,039 --> 00:45:37,468
Tunatumia mtandao wenu
labda kwa sehemu ndogo sana ya sekunde, kama...

794
00:45:37,503 --> 00:45:39,943
kama, muda mfupi zaidi ya huo.

795
00:45:39,978 --> 00:45:41,978
-Hivyo ni kiasi -- kiasi gani --
Samahani, ni vifaa vingapi --

796
00:45:42,013 --> 00:45:44,211
-Mawasiliano ya mwezi mzima
yatatumia uwezo mdogo wa mtandao

797
00:45:44,246 --> 00:45:46,884
kuliko simu moja ya kawaida ya ndani.

798
00:45:46,919 --> 00:45:48,545
Hivyo unaweza kuwa na vifaa nusu milioni
vikifanya kazi kwa wakati mmoja.

799
00:45:48,580 --> 00:45:52,450
♪♪

800
00:45:52,485 --> 00:45:57,862
♪♪

801
00:45:57,897 --> 00:46:03,065
-Tunaweza kukiona?
-Ndiyo. Basi hiki ni mfano wa awali.

802
00:46:03,100 --> 00:46:07,102
Hivyo bado safari ni ndefu kutoka,
aam...

803
00:46:07,137 --> 00:46:09,335
Aa, bado kiko mbali,
mbali sana --

804
00:46:09,370 --> 00:46:12,437
huu mfano wa awali.

805
00:46:12,472 --> 00:46:16,573
-Kwa kweli, bila shaka hiki ndicho kifaa kikubwa zaidi duniani cha kupokea ujumbe fupi.

806
00:46:16,608 --> 00:46:21,886
-Hapana, kiuhalisia hiki ndicho kifaa kidogo zaidi duniani cha barua pepe.

807
00:46:21,921 --> 00:46:25,318
♪♪

808
00:46:25,353 --> 00:46:32,358
Samahani.

809
00:46:32,393 --> 00:46:34,492
-Naona.
Hiki ni...

810
00:46:34,527 --> 00:46:36,934
Aa, hiki -- hiki --

811
00:46:36,969 --> 00:46:39,002
Ndiyo. Aa.

812
00:46:43,041 --> 00:46:47,571
-Haya, jaribu kutumia vidole gumba.
Jaribu kuchapa kwa kutumia vidole gumba.

813
00:46:47,606 --> 00:46:52,312
♪♪

814
00:46:52,347 --> 00:46:54,182
-Aa, ndiyo.

815
00:46:54,217 --> 00:46:55,986
Mnakitaje?

816
00:46:58,518 --> 00:47:00,287
♪♪

817
00:47:07,263 --> 00:47:14,466
-Kinaitwa BlackBerry,

818
00:47:14,501 --> 00:47:19,339
kinatuma na kupokea
ujumbe wa barua pepe.

819
00:47:19,374 --> 00:47:22,408
Pia ni simu ya mkononi.

820
00:47:22,443 --> 00:47:24,509
[Watazamaji wakishangilia]

821
00:47:24,544 --> 00:47:26,280
-♪ Kwa namna nyingi watazikumbuka siku nzuri za zamani ♪

822
00:47:26,315 --> 00:47:30,647
♪ Siku moja, siku moja ♪

823
00:47:30,682 --> 00:47:35,091
♪ Ndiyo, inaumiza kusema lakini nataka ubaki ♪

824
00:47:35,126 --> 00:47:39,931
♪ Wakati mwingine, wakati mwingine ♪

825
00:47:39,966 --> 00:47:44,067
♪ Tulipokuwa vijana, jamani, tulifurahia sana ♪

826
00:47:44,102 --> 00:47:48,940
♪ Daima, daima ♪

827
00:47:48,975 --> 00:47:53,340
♪ Ahadi huvunjika kabla hata hazijawekwa ♪

828
00:47:53,375 --> 00:47:57,949
♪ Wakati mwingine, wakati mwingine ♪

829
00:47:57,984 --> 00:48:01,711
-Habari za asubuhi, Bwana Balsillie.

830
00:48:01,746 --> 00:48:06,320
-♪ Nitajitahidi kadiri ya uwezo wangu ♪

831
00:48:06,355 --> 00:48:11,391
♪ Unasema unataka kuwa upande wangu ♪

832
00:48:11,426 --> 00:48:14,691
[Anazima injini]

833
00:48:14,726 --> 00:48:16,660
-Habari za asubuhi, Bwana Balsillie.
-Habari za asubuhi, Bwana Balsillie.

834
00:48:16,695 --> 00:48:19,003
-Mike amefika hapa kabla yangu?

835
00:48:19,038 --> 00:48:20,598
-Hakuondoka jana usiku.

836
00:48:20,633 --> 00:48:22,303
Umetajwa kwenye ukurasa wa tisa.

837
00:48:22,338 --> 00:48:25,438
Carl Yankowski kutoka Palm Pilot anaendelea kupiga simu.

838
00:48:25,473 --> 00:48:28,639
Ndiyo, basi mwambie kama anataka kuzungumza nami,

839
00:48:28,674 --> 00:48:30,476
anaweza kuja Waterloo.
-Hivyo ndivyo nilivyosema.

840
00:48:30,511 --> 00:48:33,281
Ted Rogers anataka tupate chakula cha mchana mjini. Ameweka nafasi kwenye mgahawa wa Canoe.

841
00:48:33,316 --> 00:48:35,481
-Hapana, hapana, siendi --
siendi Toronto kabisa

842
00:48:35,516 --> 00:48:37,747
isipokuwa kuwe na mchezo.
Ah, na upigie ofisi ya Gary Bettman

843
00:48:37,782 --> 00:48:40,288
kuhusu hizo tiketi za Leaf.

844
00:48:40,323 --> 00:48:42,059
Mpuuzi yule alijaribu kuniweka kwenye safu ya tatu.

845
00:48:42,094 --> 00:48:44,259
-"Mpuuzi yule, safu ya tatu."
Nimeelewa.

846
00:48:44,294 --> 00:48:48,263
-Haya, jaribu 114 na 114.

847
00:48:48,298 --> 00:48:53,400
-Sawa. Chagua 114.

848
00:48:53,435 --> 00:48:56,205
-Sawa. Inatuma.

849
00:48:56,240 --> 00:48:59,208
[Mlio wa vifaa, shangwe]

850
00:49:12,421 --> 00:49:14,223
-Mungu wangu. Mungu wangu.
Mungu wangu. Mungu wangu.

851
00:49:14,258 --> 00:49:18,161
Vijana!

852
00:49:18,196 --> 00:49:20,691
Imekamilika! Imekamilika! Ndiyo! Ndiyo! Haya sasa.

853
00:49:20,726 --> 00:49:24,332
-Habari. Habari, Jim.

854
00:49:24,367 --> 00:49:26,070
Ndiyo, sisi, ee,
tumeunda mfumo wa kutuma ujumbe,

855
00:49:26,105 --> 00:49:29,106
wa kutumiana ujumbe wa pande mbili
uliosimbwa kikamilifu

856
00:49:29,141 --> 00:49:31,603
ambao hauwezi kuingiliwa na mtu yeyote kabisa,

857
00:49:31,638 --> 00:49:34,771
hata sisi wenyewe.
Ni -- ni --

858
00:49:34,806 --> 00:49:37,477
haufuatiliki, hautambuliki,
haudukuliki.

859
00:49:37,512 --> 00:49:42,515
-Ni kutuma ujumbe tu.

860
00:49:44,684 --> 00:49:47,355
-Ee -- kwa hiyo -- hapana.

861
00:49:47,390 --> 00:49:49,126
Je, unajua inagharimu kiasi gani
kutuma ujumbe wa maandishi?

862
00:49:49,161 --> 00:49:51,194
-Ndiyo, senti kumi, na mtandao
unachukua kila senti.

863
00:49:51,229 --> 00:49:54,626
Hatutawahi
kuiona hiyo pesa.

864
00:49:54,661 --> 00:49:57,068
-Sawa, lakini ujumbe huu
unatumwa kupitia njia ya mtandao.

865
00:49:57,103 --> 00:50:00,302
Hivyo, ni bila mtandao kujua.
Ambayo inamaanisha...?

866
00:50:00,337 --> 00:50:04,834
-Ujumbe wa bure usio na kikomo,
kwenye BlackBerry pekee.

867
00:50:04,869 --> 00:50:08,541
Safi sana!

868
00:50:12,547 --> 00:50:15,548
-Haya!

869
00:50:15,583 --> 00:50:18,254
-Safi sana!

870
00:50:18,289 --> 00:50:20,190
♪♪

871
00:50:20,225 --> 00:50:22,390
-Nilituma ujumbe
ambao Alexander Graham Bell

872
00:50:22,425 --> 00:50:24,128
alimwambia msaidizi wake,
"Watson, njoo hapa."

873
00:50:24,163 --> 00:50:26,097
Hicho ndicho nili --
-Sawa, hebu tu --

874
00:50:26,132 --> 00:50:27,791
Hebu tu...
-Ndiyo, ndiyo.

875
00:50:27,826 --> 00:50:29,265
-♪ Oh ♪

876
00:50:29,300 --> 00:50:32,763
♪ Haya basi, ndiyo ♪

877
00:50:32,798 --> 00:50:38,208
-[Anacheka]

878
00:50:38,243 --> 00:50:41,211
Mnafanya nini
hapa ninyi?!

879
00:50:41,246 --> 00:50:43,147
-♪ Kama nilivyosema,
hadithi inaendelea ♪

880
00:50:43,182 --> 00:50:45,677
[Anakata muziki]

881
00:50:45,712 --> 00:50:50,781
-Samahani. Wewe ni nani?

882
00:50:50,816 --> 00:50:52,585
-Ulisema kama nikitaka kuzungumza,
nilipaswa kuja Waterloo.

883
00:50:52,620 --> 00:50:55,291
Basi, nimefika.

884
00:50:55,326 --> 00:50:59,460
-Waungwana...

885
00:50:59,495 --> 00:51:00,857
Mkuteni Carl Yankowski
wa Palm Pilot.

886
00:51:00,892 --> 00:51:02,859
-Oh, kweli?

887
00:51:02,894 --> 00:51:05,268
-[Anacheka]
-Doug.

888
00:51:05,303 --> 00:51:07,666
-U hali gani?

889
00:51:10,308 --> 00:51:11,835
-Basi, nikasema maneno matatu tu:
chupa ya lita mbili.

890
00:51:11,870 --> 00:51:16,378
Na unajua walichosema?
Walisema -- [Anacheka]

891
00:51:16,413 --> 00:51:22,714
"Carl, hakuna anayekunywa
lita mbili za Mountain Dew."

892
00:51:22,749 --> 00:51:28,621
Namaanisha, hawakuona
nilichokiona.

893
00:51:28,656 --> 00:51:31,492
Piza kubwa, soda kubwa,
mlo kamili.

894
00:51:31,527 --> 00:51:35,529
Tuliuza lita bilioni moja
ndani ya mwezi mmoja!

895
00:51:35,564 --> 00:51:38,763
Unajichezea huko chini,
Mikey?

896
00:51:42,472 --> 00:51:46,276
Haya, na tuweke mambo sawa hapa.

897
00:51:52,515 --> 00:51:54,482
Sikuwa na uhusiano wowote na
US Robotics

898
00:51:54,517 --> 00:51:56,748
wakijaribu kukufilisi
huko nyuma mwaka wa tisini na sita.

899
00:51:56,783 --> 00:51:58,948
Modemu mbovu,
modemu nzima.

900
00:51:58,983 --> 00:52:01,258
Je, zilikuwa na hitilafu?

901
00:52:01,293 --> 00:52:03,227
Hapana, ilikuwa miaka mia moja iliyopita.
Nani anayejua?

902
00:52:03,262 --> 00:52:05,757
-Mimi.

903
00:52:05,792 --> 00:52:08,760
-Haswa.

904
00:52:08,795 --> 00:52:11,895
Hivi ndivyo tutakavyofanya.

905
00:52:11,930 --> 00:52:14,898
Unganisha BlackBerry
na Palm Pilot,

906
00:52:14,933 --> 00:52:17,868
bidhaa moja.

907
00:52:17,903 --> 00:52:20,673
Ni chupa ya lita mbili
ya simu janja.

908
00:52:20,708 --> 00:52:24,908
-Je, bado nitakuwa na udhibiti kamilifu
wa kila nyanja

909
00:52:24,943 --> 00:52:28,846
ya uhandisi na usanifu?

910
00:52:28,881 --> 00:52:31,981
-Hapana.
Haya basi, hilo lita--

911
00:52:32,016 --> 00:52:34,951
hatutaweza kuendelea
na hili, samahani.

912
00:52:34,986 --> 00:52:38,295
Samahani.

913
00:52:38,330 --> 00:52:40,660
-Ninyi watu mnapenda kusema samahani,
au sivyo?

914
00:52:40,695 --> 00:52:45,269
Haya, hebu tuone
mlifunga kwa bei gani.

915
00:52:45,304 --> 00:52:48,272
Dola nne na senti hamsini. Ee Mungu.
Je, ni za Kanada?

916
00:52:50,375 --> 00:52:54,245
US Robotics...

917
00:52:54,280 --> 00:52:57,446
Haya, dola themanini na tatu.

918
00:52:57,481 --> 00:52:59,448
Sasa, hilo linatupatia thamani ya soko
ya takriban dola bilioni arobaini na tano.

919
00:52:59,483 --> 00:53:04,519
Hivyo nini kingetokea
kama mimi...

920
00:53:04,554 --> 00:53:06,950
Sijui,
ngenunua hisa zenu zote.

921
00:53:06,985 --> 00:53:11,328
Na ni neno gani
la hilo tena, kijana?

922
00:53:11,363 --> 00:53:14,331
Unyakuo wa kimabavu.

923
00:53:15,994 --> 00:53:19,028
-Unyakuo wa kima--
Nini hiki?

924
00:53:19,063 --> 00:53:21,338
Nini kinaendelea?

925
00:53:21,373 --> 00:53:23,340
-Tunaweza kusema tu --
tunaweza kusema hapana.

926
00:53:23,375 --> 00:53:25,441
Sisi ndio--
Sisi ndio wamiliki wa kampuni.

927
00:53:25,476 --> 00:53:27,575
-Unajua, Carl,

928
00:53:29,744 --> 00:53:32,580
tumekubaliana.
-Kweli?

929
00:53:32,615 --> 00:53:35,913
-Ndiyo. Tupe tu miezi michache
tuhakikishe watu wetu

930
00:53:35,948 --> 00:53:38,949
wanashughulikiwa
na kisha tuta, ee,

931
00:53:38,984 --> 00:53:40,522
tutakubali mauzo ya binafsi.

932
00:53:40,557 --> 00:53:42,326
-Subiri, hebu --
-Mike, haina shida.

933
00:53:42,361 --> 00:53:44,889
Ni sawa tu.
Ni bora kuwa tajiri sasa

934
00:53:44,924 --> 00:53:46,957
kuliko kupambana na mtu huyu mahakamani
kwa miaka mitano ijayo.

935
00:53:46,992 --> 00:53:49,861
-[Anacheka] Ni kweli kabisa.
Unajua, nimekupenda.

936
00:53:49,896 --> 00:53:54,338
-Unapenda hoki?

937
00:53:54,373 --> 00:53:55,900
-Mungu wangu, hapana.
Ni upumbavu.
Wewe?

938
00:53:55,935 --> 00:53:58,342
-Siupendi kabisa.

939
00:53:58,377 --> 00:54:01,576
<i>-Nimekuja hapa kutafuna</i>
<i>bigijii na kutoa kichapo.</i>

940
00:54:01,611 --> 00:54:04,579
<i>Na bigijii zote</i>
<i>zimekwisha.</i>

941
00:54:04,614 --> 00:54:12,587
-Oho, walimwiga Duke Nukem
kutoka kwa mtu huyu.

942
00:54:12,622 --> 00:54:14,325
[Milipuko ya bunduki]

943
00:54:14,360 --> 00:54:16,822
Yaani, huyo ni Duke Nukem
wa kweli.

944
00:54:16,857 --> 00:54:19,891
-Haya.
Sherehe imeisha.

945
00:54:19,926 --> 00:54:22,564
<i>-Ana bunduki ya marisau.</i>
<i>Mwanaume mweupe, mwenye umri wa miaka 30.</i>

946
00:54:28,066 --> 00:54:31,100
-Nini?
-Sikilizeni.

947
00:54:31,135 --> 00:54:33,707
Zima hicho kitu, tafadhali.

948
00:54:33,742 --> 00:54:37,348
-Subiri --
-Je, unaweza -- unaweza --

949
00:54:37,383 --> 00:54:40,483
-Kizime.

950
00:54:40,518 --> 00:54:42,914
-Al, unaweza kuisogeza?

951
00:54:42,949 --> 00:54:44,850
-Ndiyo.
-Mnafurahia?

952
00:54:44,885 --> 00:54:45,950
Kwa sababu tunakaribia kuipoteza
kampuni yetu kabisa.

953
00:54:45,985 --> 00:54:48,920
-Nini hasa kilitokea kwenye
chakula hiki cha mchana?

954
00:54:48,955 --> 00:54:51,494
-Kizime hicho kitu mara moja!

955
00:54:51,529 --> 00:54:54,563
Sawa?

956
00:54:54,598 --> 00:54:56,961
♪♪

957
00:55:04,003 --> 00:55:05,706
Ndiyo, Doug?

958
00:55:05,741 --> 00:55:11,514
-Hivyo basi, swali langu
kwa kweli ni la Mike.

959
00:55:11,549 --> 00:55:13,450
Tunatarajiwaje kuuza
simu nyingine laki tano

960
00:55:13,485 --> 00:55:16,618
wakati tayari tumefikia kikomo
kwenye kila mtandao tulio nao?

961
00:55:16,653 --> 00:55:19,115
-Nyinyi mtapata ufumbuzi.
-V-vipi?

962
00:55:19,150 --> 00:55:23,086
Tukiweka simu zaidi
kwenye mitandao hii,

963
00:55:25,860 --> 00:55:28,861
zitashindwa kufanya kazi, nukta.

964
00:55:28,896 --> 00:55:30,566
Hatujaruhusiwa
kuuza simu zaidi. Mike?

965
00:55:30,601 --> 00:55:32,865
-Hapana, usijali
kuhusu kile kinachoruhusiwa.

966
00:55:32,900 --> 00:55:35,967
Mimi ndiye ninayeamua kinachoruhusiwa.

967
00:55:36,002 --> 00:55:37,540
-Hata sielewi
tatizo ni nini hapa.

968
00:55:37,575 --> 00:55:39,036
Nani anajali kama huyu mtu
anataka kununua kampuni yetu?

969
00:55:39,071 --> 00:55:40,774
Je, hiyo siyo nzuri?
-Mimi najali sana!

970
00:55:40,809 --> 00:55:43,172
Huyo ndiye anayejali? Mimi najali!

971
00:55:43,207 --> 00:55:45,614
Najaribu kuinusuru kampuni hii,
wewe mpumbavu!

972
00:55:45,649 --> 00:55:47,781
-Samahani, hivi unajua hata
mzigo wa kikomo cha mtandao ni nini?

973
00:55:47,816 --> 00:55:50,751
-Doug...

974
00:55:50,786 --> 00:55:54,150
-Tuzungumze nje
kwa muda mfupi.

975
00:55:54,185 --> 00:55:57,593
-Nini?

976
00:55:57,628 --> 00:55:59,628
-Kiwango cha ukomo wa mzigo wa mtandao ni nini?

977
00:56:02,897 --> 00:56:04,732
-Hili haliwezekani.
-Tunapaswa kufanya

978
00:56:09,772 --> 00:56:11,937
nini sasa, Mike?
Ila ama tupandishe thamani ya hisa zetu

979
00:56:11,972 --> 00:56:14,137
hadi kileleni
au Yankowski atatuangamiza!

980
00:56:14,172 --> 00:56:16,843
-Sawa, Doug yuko sahihi.

981
00:56:16,878 --> 00:56:18,713
Isipokuwa kama watoa huduma
watajenga upya mitandao yao yote,

982
00:56:18,748 --> 00:56:20,748
hakuna tunachoweza kufanya,
simu hizi zinatumia data nyingi mno.

983
00:56:20,783 --> 00:56:23,850
-Basi, basi,
ipunguze tu.

984
00:56:23,885 --> 00:56:26,490
-Ndiyo, sawa. Hmm...

985
00:56:26,525 --> 00:56:28,151
Tuli-- tulilichunguza hilo.
-Enhe?!

986
00:56:28,186 --> 00:56:29,625
-Hawa jamaa hawawezi kulifanya.

987
00:56:29,660 --> 00:56:33,090
-Unamaanisha nini
kwamba hawawezi?

988
00:56:37,602 --> 00:56:39,767
Ulisema kuwa wao ni
wahandisi bora zaidi duniani.

989
00:56:39,802 --> 00:56:42,066
-Nilisema ni
wahandisi bora zaidi nchini Kanada.

990
00:56:42,101 --> 00:56:44,541
-Haya, basi. Sawa.

991
00:56:44,576 --> 00:56:46,972
Ni nani anayeweza kulifanya.

992
00:56:51,814 --> 00:56:54,144
-Labda wataalamu mashuhuri kutoka Motorola
au Microsoft au Google.

993
00:56:54,179 --> 00:56:56,916
-Sawa.

994
00:56:56,951 --> 00:57:01,789
-Subiri, nini? Nini? Nini?

995
00:57:01,824 --> 00:57:03,120
-Unafanya nini?
-Nani mwingine? Wapi kwingine?

996
00:57:03,155 --> 00:57:04,693
-John Carmack.

997
00:57:04,728 --> 00:57:07,531
Mtafuteni John Carmack kutoka ID.

998
00:57:07,566 --> 00:57:10,732
Je, mmenisikia?

999
00:57:10,767 --> 00:57:13,097
Yule jamaa aliyetengeneza mchezo wa "Doom."

1000
00:57:13,132 --> 00:57:14,769
- "Doom" ni nini?

1001
00:57:14,804 --> 00:57:17,233
- Je, umecheza mchezo wa "Wolfenstein"?

1002
00:57:17,268 --> 00:57:19,202
Tafadhali usiuze
simu nyingine yoyote.

1003
00:57:19,237 --> 00:57:21,105
- Unanisikia?
- Ndiyo! Ndiyo!

1004
00:57:24,550 --> 00:57:26,715
- Lahaula!

1005
00:57:30,985 --> 00:57:33,590
Haya.

1006
00:57:33,625 --> 00:57:37,088
[Muziki kwenye redio]

1007
00:57:37,123 --> 00:57:38,925
[Mazungumzo ya msisimko]

1008
00:57:40,599 --> 00:57:46,130
- Haya. Nisikilizeni,
enyi wajinga msio na akili.

1009
00:57:46,165 --> 00:57:50,739
Samahani kwa kukatisha
likizo yenu fupi hapa,

1010
00:57:50,774 --> 00:57:54,644
lakini tuna bidhaa za kusambaza.

1011
00:57:54,679 --> 00:57:57,207
- Bidhaa? Tunaweza kusambaza?
- Samahani. Umesema nini?

1012
00:57:57,242 --> 00:57:59,748
Sema tena.
- Kwani, nilidhani wahandisi

1013
00:57:59,783 --> 00:58:02,245
walisema kuwa tumefikia
ukomo wa mitandao.

1014
00:58:02,280 --> 00:58:04,280
- Ndiyo, walisema hivyo, na
hilo ni tatizo lao wenyewe.

1015
00:58:04,315 --> 00:58:06,084
Sawa? Tatizo lenu ni kwamba mnatakiwa
kuuza

1016
00:58:06,119 --> 00:58:07,987
simu milioni moja za Blackberry
kabla ya robo ya tatu ya mwaka.

1017
00:58:08,022 --> 00:58:10,561
[Kicheko]

1018
00:58:10,596 --> 00:58:12,992
- Eeh. Hiyo ni...
- "Eeh. Eeh."

1019
00:58:13,027 --> 00:58:14,961
"Eeh."

1020
00:58:17,636 --> 00:58:22,001
[Anacheka kwa kejeli]

1021
00:58:22,036 --> 00:58:23,739
Sifanyi mzaha hata kidogo.

1022
00:58:23,774 --> 00:58:26,709
Nataka zote ziishe.

1023
00:58:26,744 --> 00:58:29,206
♪♪

1024
00:58:33,652 --> 00:58:35,586
♪♪

1025
00:58:35,621 --> 00:58:42,626
♪♪

1026
00:58:42,661 --> 00:58:49,666
♪♪

1027
00:58:49,701 --> 00:58:56,673
[Milio ya ndege]

1028
00:58:56,708 --> 00:59:03,713
♪♪

1029
00:59:03,748 --> 00:59:05,209
♪♪

1030
00:59:05,244 --> 00:59:14,284
-[Anashusha pumzi] Kwa kweli, wanazungumzia kuvipiga marufuku hivi.

1031
00:59:14,319 --> 00:59:23,667
-Kuvipiga marufuku?
-Hakuna anayefuatilia tena

1032
00:59:28,971 --> 00:59:34,172
mikutano, wote wameinama tu.

1033
00:59:34,207 --> 00:59:36,009
-Waambie waache.
-[Anacheka] Haya.

1034
00:59:36,044 --> 00:59:38,715
Tunaziita 'Crackberry'.

1035
00:59:38,750 --> 00:59:41,014
-Njoo unifanyie kazi.
-[Anaguna]

1036
00:59:41,049 --> 00:59:45,051
Siwezi.
-Kwa nini?

1037
00:59:45,086 --> 00:59:47,416
-Kwa sababu niko kwenye mkataba hapa.

1038
00:59:47,451 --> 00:59:50,419
-Ni kiasi gani kuuvunja?

1039
00:59:50,454 --> 00:59:53,862
-Samahani?

1040
00:59:53,897 --> 00:59:56,227
-Unataka kiasi gani cha fedha

1041
00:59:56,262 --> 00:59:57,800
ili uvunje mkataba wako na Google?

1042
00:59:57,835 --> 00:59:59,164
Mimi --
[Anasafisha koo]

1043
00:59:59,199 --> 01:00:01,936
-Nitakupa dola milioni moja ukisaini sasa hivi.

1044
01:00:01,971 --> 01:00:03,773
-Sihamii nchini Kanada.

1045
01:00:09,407 --> 01:00:12,947
Hatutaendelea na mazungumzo haya.

1046
01:00:12,982 --> 01:00:14,443
-Dola milioni mbili.
-Acha.

1047
01:00:14,478 --> 01:00:16,885
-Dola milioni tatu.
-Nakuomba uondoke.

1048
01:00:16,920 --> 01:00:18,689
-Dola milioni kumi.

1049
01:00:18,724 --> 01:00:21,186
-Sawa, huna
dola milioni kumi.

1050
01:00:26,325 --> 01:00:28,127
-Huu ni mkataba wa hiari wa dola milioni moja.

1051
01:00:32,298 --> 01:00:34,936
Nitarudisha tarehe hiyo hadi wakati
RIM ilipokuwa inauzwa kwa dola moja.

1052
01:00:38,073 --> 01:00:42,273
Merrill ametupa
lengo la dola kumi na tatu.

1053
01:00:42,308 --> 01:00:46,145
-Je, jambo hili ni halali?

1054
01:00:46,180 --> 01:00:49,115
[Muziki wa kielektroniki unacheza]

1055
01:00:53,924 --> 01:00:55,858
-Carl!
<i>-Palm-Berry!</i>

1056
01:00:58,258 --> 01:01:03,261
-Ndiyo. -Hebu sikiliza, nina
shida kukusikia, rafiki yangu.

1057
01:01:03,296 --> 01:01:05,230
<i>-Nimesema Palm-Berry,</i>
<i>je, si hiyo ni nzuri?</i>

1058
01:01:05,265 --> 01:01:07,837
-Sikiliza, kuna
mikwaruzo kwenye simu.

1059
01:01:07,872 --> 01:01:09,971
Naweza, uh -- naweza --
naweza kukupigia baadaye?

1060
01:01:10,006 --> 01:01:13,139
<i>-Sikusikii vizuri kabisa.</i>

1061
01:01:13,174 --> 01:01:15,504
-Nini -- Carl?
Sawa. Nitakupigia baadaye.

1062
01:01:15,539 --> 01:01:18,210
♪♪

1063
01:01:18,245 --> 01:01:22,346
[Mlio wa kifaa]

1064
01:01:22,381 --> 01:01:28,792
♪♪

1065
01:01:28,827 --> 01:01:31,454
♪♪

1066
01:01:31,489 --> 01:01:38,131
♪♪

1067
01:01:38,166 --> 01:01:44,808
♪♪

1068
01:01:44,843 --> 01:01:51,243
-[Sauti isiyoeleweka]
-Mike? Mike Lazaridis

1069
01:01:51,278 --> 01:01:57,920
-Uh, sawa. Ikiwa Jim alikufuta kazi,
siwezi kubadilisha hilo.

1070
01:01:57,955 --> 01:02:00,318
Samahani. Nimejaribu.
-Hapana, hapana. Nimeajiriwa hivi punde.

1071
01:02:00,353 --> 01:02:03,860
Ni Paul.
-Hujambo? Karibu.

1072
01:02:03,895 --> 01:02:06,929
Unatokea wapi?
-Google.

1073
01:02:06,964 --> 01:02:08,458
-Safi sana. Ulikuwa unafanya nini?

1074
01:02:08,493 --> 01:02:10,361
-Nilikuwa, ee, mkuu wa
uhandisi wa miundo.

1075
01:02:10,396 --> 01:02:13,903
♪♪

1076
01:02:13,938 --> 01:02:16,103
-Ninyi si wauzaji tena.

1077
01:02:16,138 --> 01:02:23,506
Ninyi ni wanamitindo wa kiume.

1078
01:02:23,541 --> 01:02:26,344
Nataka muwe katika kila
klabu ya kifahari, klabu ya mashua,

1079
01:02:26,379 --> 01:02:28,346
klabu ya tenisi,
popote pale tabaka la juu linapoenda, nanyi nendeni.

1080
01:02:28,381 --> 01:02:31,954
Nataka wawaone mkitumia.

1081
01:02:31,989 --> 01:02:35,925
[Mlio wa kengele]

1082
01:02:35,960 --> 01:02:37,993
Iweni mashuhuri. Jitokezeni.

1083
01:02:38,028 --> 01:02:39,995
Wafanye wafikirie,
"Huyu kero msumbufu ni nani,

1084
01:02:40,030 --> 01:02:43,262
na nawezaje kuwa kama yeye?"

1085
01:02:43,297 --> 01:02:45,330
-[Kicheko]
-Ni nini hicho?

1086
01:02:45,365 --> 01:02:47,464
-Na watakapowauliza,
usiseme,

1087
01:02:47,499 --> 01:02:49,499
"Ni simu
inayotuma barua pepe."

1088
01:02:49,534 --> 01:02:50,973
Hii siyo simu ya mkononi tu.

1089
01:02:51,008 --> 01:02:53,976
Ni ishara ya hadhi.

1090
01:02:54,011 --> 01:02:56,407
-Kuna mwingine yeyote?
Mwingine yeyote? Haya.

1091
01:02:56,442 --> 01:02:58,409
♪♪

1092
01:03:02,085 --> 01:03:04,019
-Habari, napiga simu kwa niaba
ya BlackBerry.

1093
01:03:04,054 --> 01:03:07,055
Nimesikia kwamba mna nia
ya kununua baadhi ya Quark

1094
01:03:07,090 --> 01:03:09,585
kwa ajili ya shirika lenu.

1095
01:03:09,620 --> 01:03:12,929
♪♪

1096
01:03:12,964 --> 01:03:14,964
♪♪

1097
01:03:14,999 --> 01:03:23,104
♪♪

1098
01:03:23,139 --> 01:03:31,211
-Ni saa moja na dakika hamsini na tano. Tumerudi
na Habari za Walaji za Fox 5.

1099
01:03:31,246 --> 01:03:39,351
Mgogoro wa BlackBerry ulimwenguni kote asubuhi ya leo.

1100
01:03:39,386 --> 01:03:42,057
Kampuni inasema kuwa inakumbwa na hitilafu kubwa

1101
01:03:42,092 --> 01:03:44,323
ya kukatika kwa huduma.

1102
01:03:44,358 --> 01:03:46,963
Huduma kwa wateja ya kampuni inasema kuwa watumiaji wategemee ucheleweshaji

1103
01:03:46,998 --> 01:03:48,558
wa kutuma na kupokea ujumbe.

1104
01:03:48,593 --> 01:03:51,363
-Ndiyo, ndiyo, tunafahamu tatizo lililopo

1105
01:03:51,398 --> 01:03:53,970
na tuna—tunalitatua hivi sasa.

1106
01:03:54,005 --> 01:03:56,038
-Huduma imekatika kule, Dougie.

1107
01:03:56,073 --> 01:03:58,909
-Tumewahi kukatika kwa muda mrefu hivi hapo awali.

1108
01:03:58,944 --> 01:04:00,372
Je, mambo yameharibika kabisa? -Hebu! Nyamazeni!

1109
01:04:00,407 --> 01:04:03,177
♪♪

1110
01:04:03,212 --> 01:04:07,643
-H-hebu tupunguze sauti hapa nje, jamani, kwa muda kidogo.

1111
01:04:07,678 --> 01:04:11,988
-Ni ngapi hazifanyi kazi?

1112
01:04:12,023 --> 01:04:16,124
-Labda elfu kumi.

1113
01:04:17,622 --> 01:04:20,194
-Lo, Mungu wangu. Sawa.

1114
01:04:20,229 --> 01:04:22,658
Sawa. [Mlio wa simu]

1115
01:04:22,693 --> 01:04:24,495
Sawa. Sawa. Halo?

1116
01:04:24,530 --> 01:04:26,365
<i>-Una simu ya malipo kutoka kwa--</i> <i>-Nini kinaendelea hapa?!</i>

1117
01:04:26,400 --> 01:04:30,567
<i>-Je, utakubali kulipia gharama?</i>

1118
01:04:30,602 --> 01:04:34,076
<i>Bado upo?</i> -Ndiyo, nakubali.

1119
01:04:34,111 --> 01:04:37,607
<i>-Asante.</i> <i>-Mike?!</i>

1120
01:04:37,642 --> 01:04:40,346
-Habari. -Kuna sababu tatu kwa nini

1121
01:04:40,381 --> 01:04:42,150
watu hununua simu zetu, je, unazijua ni zipi?

1122
01:04:42,185 --> 01:04:44,482
-Kwa ajili ya barua pepe. -Zinafanya kazi kikamilifu.

1123
01:04:44,517 --> 01:04:46,649
-Ndiyo. Sawa. Sio sisi, Jim. Ni mtoa huduma wa mawasiliano.

1124
01:04:46,684 --> 01:04:50,554
Verizon wanafanya jambo fulani la ajabu.

1125
01:04:50,589 --> 01:04:53,293
-Basi, nami niko karibu kufanya jambo la ajabu

1126
01:04:53,328 --> 01:04:54,723
ikiwa hutarekebisha hili sasa hivi!

1127
01:04:54,758 --> 01:04:56,395
Makubaliano yalikuwa kwamba mimi nipate wahandisi,

1128
01:04:56,430 --> 01:04:58,034
nawe upunguze ukubwa wa data. -Je, unawa-- unawa--

1129
01:04:58,069 --> 01:05:01,004
Je, unauza simu zaidi? -Unadhani nimekuwa nikifanya nini

1130
01:05:01,039 --> 01:05:02,698
hapa kwa muda wote huu, Mike!

1131
01:05:02,733 --> 01:05:05,437
Tuko katikati ya mchakato mkali wa unyakuzi wa kampuni.

1132
01:05:05,472 --> 01:05:07,142
Je, nahitaji mtu wa kuwalea ninyi mabwege?!

1133
01:05:07,177 --> 01:05:09,375
-Sawa. Sawa. Hivyo ndivyo -- Sawa, haya.

1134
01:05:09,410 --> 01:05:12,147
Mfumo mzima unaharibika. Anauza simu zaidi.

1135
01:05:12,182 --> 01:05:15,678
-Hebu, jamani! -Ndiyo. Ndiyo.

1136
01:05:15,713 --> 01:05:19,253
Haya, basi.

1137
01:05:19,288 --> 01:05:21,684
Unajua, labda uache kwanza kuuza simu zai--

1138
01:05:21,719 --> 01:05:23,752
-Sifa-- Mungu wangu!

1139
01:05:23,787 --> 01:05:26,689
[Mshindo]

1140
01:05:26,724 --> 01:05:28,427
-Sawa. Samahani. Je, kisheria jambo hili linaruhusiwa?

1141
01:05:28,462 --> 01:05:34,433
-Eugene!

1142
01:05:48,647 --> 01:05:52,088
-Kwa kweli niko kwenye mkutano wa binafsi, Charles.

1143
01:05:52,123 --> 01:05:54,255
-Na mimi binafsi sijali hata kidogo.

1144
01:05:54,290 --> 01:05:56,389
Wahandisi hawawezi kufanya chochote mpaka utume hiyo faksi.

1145
01:05:56,424 --> 01:05:58,490
Sasa, fanya mkutano wakati chama cha wafanyakazi hakinitia shinikizo.

1146
01:05:58,525 --> 01:06:02,494
Unanisikia?

1147
01:06:02,529 --> 01:06:07,367
Ikamilishe.

1148
01:06:07,402 --> 01:06:09,171
Pumbavu kabisa.

1149
01:06:11,835 --> 01:06:15,111
-Ulisema mko Waterloo.

1150
01:06:15,146 --> 01:06:17,476
-Jina la huyo jamaa ni nani?

1151
01:06:21,383 --> 01:06:24,219
-Ndiyo. Sawa.

1152
01:06:26,289 --> 01:06:28,355
Sawa. Sawa. Hujambo kila mmoja. Karibuni katika Research in Motion.

1153
01:06:28,390 --> 01:06:30,357
Najua mambo hayajajipanga vizuri hapa.

1154
01:06:30,392 --> 01:06:33,261
Naahidi kwamba kila mtu atatulia na kupata nafasi yake.

1155
01:06:33,296 --> 01:06:35,230
Hivyo kwa sasa, tuna itilafu kidogo ya mtandao,

1156
01:06:35,265 --> 01:06:37,100
Hivyo nyoosha mkono wako kama unaelewa

1157
01:06:37,135 --> 01:06:42,237
muundo wa MOBITEX.

1158
01:06:42,272 --> 01:06:44,107
Watu wawili.

1159
01:06:44,142 --> 01:06:46,472
Sawa. Haina shida.

1160
01:06:48,641 --> 01:06:50,443
Nyinyi wawili, mtakuwa na Mike.

1161
01:06:50,478 --> 01:06:53,248
Wengine mliobaki, sijui nini kazi yenu,

1162
01:06:53,283 --> 01:06:55,382
lakini nifuateni, tunakwenda kutembelea ofisi.

1163
01:06:55,417 --> 01:06:57,714
Twendeni. Itakuwa kidogo

1164
01:06:57,749 --> 01:07:00,255
kama Sam Rockwell katika 'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles'.

1165
01:07:00,290 --> 01:07:02,851
-Naomba kuzungumza nawe kidogo?

1166
01:07:02,886 --> 01:07:05,425
Charles Purdy anafanya nini hapa?

1167
01:07:05,460 --> 01:07:08,824
-Nitachukua diski ya DVD. -Unazungumzia nini?

1168
01:07:08,859 --> 01:07:10,826
-Yule mwanaume aliyesimama ukumbini

1169
01:07:10,861 --> 01:07:13,400
moja kwa moja nyuma ya bega langu la kushoto.

1170
01:07:13,435 --> 01:07:15,138
-Mungu wangu. -Nisikilize.

1171
01:07:15,173 --> 01:07:18,372
Huyo jamaa atakuharibia kila kitu.

1172
01:07:18,407 --> 01:07:21,474
Usimruhusu mtu huyo kukaribia kabisa

1173
01:07:21,509 --> 01:07:24,279
idara yako ya uhandisi. Niamini.

1174
01:07:24,314 --> 01:07:26,413
-Ndiyo, sawa. Ndiyo. Haya.

1175
01:07:26,448 --> 01:07:29,878
-Nazungumza kwa dhati.

1176
01:07:29,913 --> 01:07:33,651
Atakuvurugia mambo yako kabisa.

1177
01:07:33,686 --> 01:07:35,488
-Nikusaidie?

1178
01:07:37,426 --> 01:07:39,789
-Wewe ni Mike, sivyo?

1179
01:07:39,824 --> 01:07:42,264
-Ndiyo, mimi ni Mike.
Unafanya nini hapa?

1180
01:07:42,299 --> 01:07:44,761
-Charles Purdy.
Mimi ni Mkurugenzi wako mpya wa Uendeshaji.

1181
01:07:44,796 --> 01:07:48,237
-Ooh.
Jim alikuajiri kuwa --

1182
01:07:48,272 --> 01:07:52,373
Mkuu...
-Niko hapa kukiweka chombo hiki

1183
01:07:52,408 --> 01:07:56,443
katika hali ya udhibiti.

1184
01:07:56,478 --> 01:07:59,182
-Mambo yako sawa hapa.

1185
01:07:59,217 --> 01:08:01,910
-Ooh, kweli? Chini ya nani?

1186
01:08:01,945 --> 01:08:03,846
Hmm?

1187
01:08:03,881 --> 01:08:07,421
-Sawa, basi hebu tujaribu
kitu kingine tofauti.

1188
01:08:17,796 --> 01:08:20,269
Badala ya kupunguza ukubwa wa taarifa,
labda tuzitawanye.

1189
01:08:27,872 --> 01:08:29,707
Asante.

1190
01:08:29,742 --> 01:08:33,282
-Basi, kwa nini tusitumie minara
mbalimbali katika eneo moja

1191
01:08:33,317 --> 01:08:35,251
na kugawanya kifurushi cha taarifa
baina ya minara hiyo?

1192
01:08:35,286 --> 01:08:37,550
Tunaweza kukiunganisha tena
kwenye seva.

1193
01:08:37,585 --> 01:08:39,420
-Tulijaribu hilo.
Tatizo ni hili.

1194
01:08:39,455 --> 01:08:40,751
Minara hiyo haitambuani.

1195
01:08:40,786 --> 01:08:42,456
Kila mmoja hauna habari ni sehemu gani
ya mawimbi unayopokea.

1196
01:08:42,491 --> 01:08:44,260
Na mchakato mzima
unazidi tu kukwama.

1197
01:08:44,295 --> 01:08:46,922
-Labda tuipangilie upya
minara hiyo.

1198
01:08:46,957 --> 01:08:48,594
-Hiyo si minara yetu.
Hatuna mamlaka nayo.

1199
01:08:48,629 --> 01:08:49,958
-Haina shida.
Kule Naughty Dog, tulilazimika
kudukua PlayStation ili kuifanya
"Crash Bandicoot" ifanye kazi.

1200
01:08:49,993 --> 01:08:52,235
-Sawa, kwa hiyo ikiwa kila mabadilishano
yanaainishwa kwa vinu vitatu,

1201
01:08:52,270 --> 01:08:54,237
tunaweza kugawa
ishara mara tatu.

1202
01:08:54,272 --> 01:08:56,767
-Kwa kweli tunaweza kufanya mengi
zaidi ya hapo.

1203
01:08:56,802 --> 01:09:00,606
Kila BlackBerry ni seva.

1204
01:09:00,641 --> 01:09:02,509
-Tunaweza kugawa ishara
baina ya kila mtumiaji

1205
01:09:02,544 --> 01:09:04,346
katika gridi ileile --
-Igawe mara maelfu.

1206
01:09:04,381 --> 01:09:05,809
Itakuwa kama Napster --
mtandao uliosambazwa

1207
01:09:05,844 --> 01:09:08,218
wa watumiaji wako mwenyewe.
-Ni lazima iwe katika

1208
01:09:08,253 --> 01:09:09,615
masharti ya huduma,
wadukuaji wataivamia haraka sana.

1209
01:09:09,650 --> 01:09:11,716
-Lakini wanasimba kila kitu
upande wa seva, sivyo?

1210
01:09:11,751 --> 01:09:13,553
Mike? Namaanisha,
kila kitu kimeshasimbwa.

1211
01:09:13,588 --> 01:09:15,852
-Mike?

1212
01:09:15,887 --> 01:09:19,691
Mike.

1213
01:09:19,726 --> 01:09:25,235
♪♪

1214
01:09:25,270 --> 01:09:27,996
-Unaweza kuchukua bekoni yangu.

1215
01:09:28,031 --> 01:09:29,734
-Wanakulipa kiasi gani?

1216
01:09:29,769 --> 01:09:35,278
-Sipaswi kusema.

1217
01:09:35,313 --> 01:09:37,412
-Wananilipa dola milioni kumi.
-Naam, nami pia.

1218
01:09:44,047 --> 01:09:45,948
♪♪

1219
01:09:45,983 --> 01:09:49,523
♪♪

1220
01:09:49,558 --> 01:09:52,625
-Shika bango lako. Lishike.

1221
01:09:59,436 --> 01:10:04,472
Na sasa.

1222
01:10:04,507 --> 01:10:09,510
[Makelele yasiyoeleweka]

1223
01:10:09,545 --> 01:10:11,809
Pandisha juu zaidi upande ule.
-Hebu tulete kiti pale.

1224
01:10:11,844 --> 01:10:13,811
♪♪

1225
01:10:13,846 --> 01:10:17,287
-Chukua hii, rafiki.

1226
01:10:17,322 --> 01:10:19,751
[Kugonga mlango]
-Ndiyo. Karibu ndani.

1227
01:10:19,786 --> 01:10:24,822
-Bwana Purdy.

1228
01:10:24,857 --> 01:10:26,626
Ndiyo, ee, basi...

1229
01:10:29,961 --> 01:10:33,336
Kwanza kabisa,
samahani kwa yaliyotokea awali.

1230
01:10:33,371 --> 01:10:36,834
[Mazungumzo yasiyoeleweka]

1231
01:10:36,869 --> 01:10:39,738
-Alan Lewis.

1232
01:10:39,773 --> 01:10:42,070
Ni nani kati yenu
aliye Alan Lewis?

1233
01:10:42,105 --> 01:10:44,479
Ah, Michael amepata
ugunduzi mkubwa.

1234
01:10:50,355 --> 01:10:53,389
Sasa nataka hizi zipimwe,

1235
01:10:53,424 --> 01:10:56,623
na nataka ripoti iwe
mezani kwangu Ijumaa.

1236
01:10:56,658 --> 01:11:00,330
-Lini? Samahani.

1237
01:11:00,365 --> 01:11:01,892
-Ijumaa.

1238
01:11:01,927 --> 01:11:05,896
-Huu unaonekana kama mfumo
mpya kabisa wa kielektroniki.

1239
01:11:05,931 --> 01:11:09,636
Kupima mfumo huu kunaweza
kunichukua mwezi mmoja.

1240
01:11:09,671 --> 01:11:11,770
-Basi, ni heri
uanze sasa, sivyo?

1241
01:11:11,805 --> 01:11:15,741
-Ni mkosi kufanya kazi
usiku wa filamu.

1242
01:11:15,776 --> 01:11:18,975
-Kufanya kazi usiku wa filamu...

1243
01:11:19,010 --> 01:11:21,714
-Ninyi nyote ni watoto.
Ndivyo ilivyo?

1244
01:11:24,653 --> 01:11:29,392
-Samahani. Wewe ni nani?

1245
01:11:29,427 --> 01:11:32,626
-Unadhani hili ni jambo la kuchekesha?!

1246
01:11:32,661 --> 01:11:36,498
Ndivyo?!

1247
01:11:36,533 --> 01:11:37,664
-Sikumaanisha -- nilitaka tu kujua,
wewe -- wewe ni nani?

1248
01:11:37,699 --> 01:11:39,061
-Mimi ni Charles Purdy.

1249
01:11:39,096 --> 01:11:40,634
Kuanzia wakati huu,
ninyi nyote mnafanya kazi kwangu.

1250
01:11:42,836 --> 01:11:45,606
Na ikiwa kazi hiyo haitafanyika
kwa kasi ninayotarajia,

1251
01:11:45,641 --> 01:11:47,575
mtafutwa kazi.

1252
01:11:47,610 --> 01:11:50,072
Na nitaendelea kufukuza watu
hadi chumba hiki kijae wanaume

1253
01:11:50,107 --> 01:11:54,813
na si wavulana wadogo wanaochezea
uume wao mdogo.

1254
01:11:54,848 --> 01:11:57,145
Sasa, kuna maswali yoyote?

1255
01:11:57,180 --> 01:12:00,819
-Eee.

1256
01:12:00,854 --> 01:12:04,889
Doug yuko wapi?

1257
01:12:11,601 --> 01:12:13,898
-♪ Hivi ndivyo tunafanya ♪

1258
01:12:16,001 --> 01:12:18,474
♪ Fanya, fanya, fanya ♪

1259
01:12:18,509 --> 01:12:20,168
♪ Mwili wangu ni mwili wangu ♪

1260
01:12:20,203 --> 01:12:22,478
♪ Muda wangu ni muda wangu ♪

1261
01:12:22,513 --> 01:12:25,008
♪ Jinsi inavyokuja kawaida
kutoka akilini mwangu ♪

1262
01:12:25,043 --> 01:12:29,078
-Doug! Mambo vipi, kaka?

1263
01:12:29,113 --> 01:12:30,882
-Usiku wa filamu leo.
Usiku wa filamu.

1264
01:12:30,917 --> 01:12:32,818
-♪ Hakuna muda wa kukaa na kusubiri,
tunafanya kile tunachofanya ♪

1265
01:12:32,853 --> 01:12:34,787
♪ Na kile tunachofanya hakiwezi kusubiri ♪

1266
01:12:34,822 --> 01:12:37,856
♪ Hivi ndivyo tunafanya ♪

1267
01:12:37,891 --> 01:12:39,594
♪ Fanya, fanya, fanya ♪

1268
01:12:39,629 --> 01:12:40,925
[Anazima injini]

1269
01:12:40,960 --> 01:12:42,465
[Muziki hafifu
kutoka kwenye vichwa vya sauti]

1270
01:12:42,500 --> 01:12:45,094
-Je, umeona hii?

1271
01:12:45,129 --> 01:12:46,568
-Hapana.
-Je, umekuwa huko nje?

1272
01:12:48,638 --> 01:12:54,609
-Hapana.

1273
01:13:27,809 --> 01:13:29,479
Mshikaji, Jim ameharibu usiku wa filamu!
Kwani, nasema nini mimi?

1274
01:13:29,514 --> 01:13:31,173
Hakuwa na ujasiri
wa kufanya hivyo mwenyewe.

1275
01:13:31,208 --> 01:13:33,010
Inavyoonekana alimpata
jamaa huyu mwenye kilo mia moja na thelathini

1276
01:13:33,045 --> 01:13:36,519
ili aingie humo, aanze kuwafokea
kila mtu,

1277
01:13:36,554 --> 01:13:37,751
akasema kwamba angemfuta kazi Alan.

1278
01:13:37,786 --> 01:13:40,622
Mike.

1279
01:13:40,657 --> 01:13:42,756
-Tunapaswa -- tunapaswa
kurejea kazini.

1280
01:13:42,791 --> 01:13:44,560
-Ndiyo.

1281
01:13:53,296 --> 01:13:55,901
♪♪

1282
01:13:55,936 --> 01:13:58,706
♪♪

1283
01:14:12,117 --> 01:14:13,820
Je, huwahi kujiuliza
kwa nini watu hawa wako tayari

1284
01:14:13,855 --> 01:14:18,891
kufanya kazi saa themanini kwa wiki,

1285
01:14:18,926 --> 01:14:23,962
bila kuona familia zao,

1286
01:14:23,997 --> 01:14:27,834
na bila kupongezwa kamwe?

1287
01:14:27,869 --> 01:14:30,034
-Ni kwa sababu
wanapata fursa ya kuunda

1288
01:14:30,069 --> 01:14:33,235
simu bora zaidi duniani,
Doug.

1289
01:14:33,270 --> 01:14:35,105
♪♪

1290
01:14:35,140 --> 01:14:36,678
-Itakuwa hivyo.

1291
01:14:36,713 --> 01:14:38,944
♪♪

1292
01:14:38,979 --> 01:14:48,723
♪♪

1293
01:14:48,758 --> 01:14:50,626
♪♪

1294
01:14:50,661 --> 01:14:55,059
[Simu inaita]
-Halo?

1295
01:14:55,094 --> 01:14:59,701
<i>-Unafanya</i>
<i>makosa makubwa, rafiki.</i>

1296
01:14:59,736 --> 01:15:03,298
-Ndiyo, samahani --
<i>-Usithubutu hata kidogo</i>

1297
01:15:03,333 --> 01:15:05,608
<i>-kunikatia simu.</i>
-Nitakupigia baadaye.

1298
01:15:05,643 --> 01:15:07,071
<i>-Usinikatie simu.</i>
<i>Usithubutu hata kidogo --</i>

1299
01:15:07,106 --> 01:15:09,040
-Habari zenu nyote?

1300
01:15:09,075 --> 01:15:10,745
-Jim.

1301
01:15:10,780 --> 01:15:12,307
Najua haya siyo hasa
unayotaka kusikia,

1302
01:15:12,342 --> 01:15:15,343
lakini bodi hii inaona kuwa

1303
01:15:15,378 --> 01:15:17,015
ili kuepuka
usumbufu zaidi,

1304
01:15:17,050 --> 01:15:19,754
ni bora tusitishe
ushirikiano wetu na BlackBerry.

1305
01:15:19,789 --> 01:15:22,790
-John, ndiyo kwanza
tunaanza.

1306
01:15:22,825 --> 01:15:25,991
-Jim, nazungumza kwa dhati.

1307
01:15:26,026 --> 01:15:29,797
Tuko tayari kukubali hasara
ya watumiaji

1308
01:15:29,832 --> 01:15:31,799
na kuwaacha waende kuvuruga
mtandao wa mtu mwingine.

1309
01:15:31,834 --> 01:15:34,637
Yamekwisha.

1310
01:15:34,672 --> 01:15:36,133
-Hapana.

1311
01:15:36,168 --> 01:15:38,102
Kilichoisha ni ule ukomo wenu
wa kipuuzi wa watumiaji laki tano.

1312
01:15:38,137 --> 01:15:41,171
Tumeuongeza mara nne.
-Sawa, Jim --

1313
01:15:41,206 --> 01:15:44,273
-Wahandisi wetu
wamebadili mifumo ya minara yenu.

1314
01:15:44,308 --> 01:15:48,618
Kufikia sasa,
Verizon ina uwezo

1315
01:15:48,653 --> 01:15:51,918
wa kuhudumia simu milioni mbili
za BlackBerry kwa wakati mmoja,

1316
01:15:51,953 --> 01:15:55,625
na tayari tumeshauza
nusu ya hizo.

1317
01:15:55,660 --> 01:15:57,319
-Upuuzi.

1318
01:15:57,354 --> 01:15:59,926
-Nijaribu uone.

1319
01:15:59,961 --> 01:16:03,193
♪♪

1320
01:16:03,228 --> 01:16:05,030
♪♪

1321
01:16:05,065 --> 01:16:07,098
♪♪

1322
01:16:11,742 --> 01:16:17,009
-♪ Habari, mhudumu ♪

1323
01:16:17,044 --> 01:16:22,278
♪ Je, unaweza kunipa namba tisa? ♪

1324
01:16:22,313 --> 01:16:27,789
♪ Naweza kukuona baadaye? ♪

1325
01:16:27,824 --> 01:16:30,121
♪ Je, utanirudishia
senti yangu ♪

1326
01:16:30,156 --> 01:16:31,727
♪ Zungusha kidhibiti-mawimbi ♪

1327
01:16:31,762 --> 01:16:34,961
♪ Izungushe kwa
noti ya dola ♪

1328
01:16:34,996 --> 01:16:37,832
♪ Msambaza barua leta karatasi ♪

1329
01:16:37,867 --> 01:16:39,999
♪ Iache kwenye kingo ya dirisha langu ♪

1330
01:16:40,034 --> 01:16:42,705
-Ulifanyaje hivyo, Mike?

1331
01:16:42,740 --> 01:16:44,971
♪♪

1332
01:16:45,006 --> 01:16:49,008
♪♪

1333
01:16:49,043 --> 01:16:50,944
♪♪

1334
01:16:50,979 --> 01:16:55,949
-Sisi ni namba moja
katika mauzo ya simu,

1335
01:16:55,984 --> 01:17:00,987
uandikishaji,
kudumisha wateja,

1336
01:17:01,022 --> 01:17:05,992
kuvutia watumiaji wapya wa simu janja,
na utambulisho wa chapa.

1337
01:17:06,027 --> 01:17:08,225
Tunamiliki asilimia 30
ya soko la Amerika Kaskazini.

1338
01:17:08,260 --> 01:17:10,293
Na kwa uzinduzi ujao
wa BlackBerry Bold --

1339
01:17:10,328 --> 01:17:14,330
[Mtetemo]
...tuko njiani kumiliki

1340
01:17:14,365 --> 01:17:17,234
asilimia 50 ya soko la dunia.

1341
01:17:17,269 --> 01:17:19,907
Sasa, takwimu zetu ziko chini kidogo
ya makadirio yetu kwa sasa,

1342
01:17:19,942 --> 01:17:21,909
lakini tunatarajia ongezeko zuri

1343
01:17:21,944 --> 01:17:23,878
wakati 8310
itakapotoka mwezi Machi.

1344
01:17:23,913 --> 01:17:29,752
-Sasa labda ni
wakati mzuri wa kuzungumzia

1345
01:17:29,787 --> 01:17:32,216
kuhamishia baadhi ya uunganishaji
na ujenzi nchini Uchina.

1346
01:17:32,251 --> 01:17:34,724
-Hapana, hapana.
Watoe watu kwenye mradi wa Onyx,

1347
01:17:34,759 --> 01:17:37,419
kama unahitaji nguvu kazi zaidi,
ajiri watu wengi zaidi.

1348
01:17:37,454 --> 01:17:41,192
Hatuhamii Uchina
kwa namna yoyote ile.

1349
01:17:41,227 --> 01:17:43,733
-Sawa.
-Sawa.

1350
01:17:43,768 --> 01:17:44,965
Mungu wangu.

1351
01:17:45,000 --> 01:17:48,837
Nini?!

1352
01:17:48,872 --> 01:17:52,236
Hapo ni sehemu nzuri ya kuishia
kwa leo, jamani, asanteni.

1353
01:17:52,271 --> 01:17:54,205
-Hivi, Jim yuko wapi?

1354
01:17:54,240 --> 01:17:56,977
-Kwani nini?
-Hajibu barua pepe zangu.

1355
01:17:57,012 --> 01:17:59,474
-Sawa, tunawasilisha wazo la
kiguso kwa kampuni ya Verizon Ijumaa,

1356
01:18:03,821 --> 01:18:06,415
hivyo pengine
anashughulikia hilo.

1357
01:18:06,450 --> 01:18:10,188
Niko kwenye kikao!

1358
01:18:10,223 --> 01:18:12,795
<i>-Na ninaamini kabisa kwamba</i>

1359
01:18:12,830 --> 01:18:15,457
<i>Vasily --</i>
'<i>ndivyo unavyolitaja?</i>

1360
01:18:15,492 --> 01:18:16,898
<i>Au kitu kama hicho?</i>
<i>Unajua, alikuwa humo ndani.</i>

1361
01:18:16,933 --> 01:18:18,768
<i>Anasema, nimeshasikia watu wakilikosea</i>
<i>jina langu, lakini si vibaya kama wewe.</i>

1362
01:18:18,803 --> 01:18:20,330
<i>Hata hivyo, yeye ni mzalendo.</i>
<i>Kwa kweli ana --</i>

1363
01:18:20,365 --> 01:18:22,299
<i>Yeye ni mpenzi wa hoki</i>
<i>ambaye kweli anataka --</i>

1364
01:18:22,334 --> 01:18:24,268
<i>hakuna pesa nyingi.</i>
<i>Hiyo haimaanishi --</i>

1365
01:18:24,303 --> 01:18:27,271
<i>Yeye ni mchezaji wa hoki. Anacheza...</i>

1366
01:18:27,306 --> 01:18:29,977
[Simu inaita]

1367
01:18:30,012 --> 01:18:32,408
-Hapana, usifanye hivyo!
[Anashusha pumzi]

1368
01:18:32,443 --> 01:18:35,081
-Halo?

1369
01:18:35,116 --> 01:18:40,152
<i>-Mpe Jim simu hiyo.</i>

1370
01:18:40,187 --> 01:18:44,057
-Ni nani huyu?
<i>-Ni Jack Manishen</i>

1371
01:18:44,092 --> 01:18:45,058
<i>wa idara ya masoko --</i>
<i>ni muhimu.</i>

1372
01:18:45,093 --> 01:18:47,093
-Jack Manishen, masoko.

1373
01:18:47,128 --> 01:18:48,930
-Ndiyo, Mike anaweza kulishughulikia.

1374
01:18:48,965 --> 01:18:51,130
-Labda unaweza kuzungumza na Bwana Lazaridis.

1375
01:18:53,431 --> 01:18:55,838
<i>-Hataki niende kwa Mike na jambo hili.</i>

1376
01:18:55,873 --> 01:18:57,807
<i>Angalau niambie unakoenda.</i>

1377
01:19:00,009 --> 01:19:02,075
-Anataka kujua tunakoenda.

1378
01:19:02,110 --> 01:19:04,814
-Kata simu.

1379
01:19:07,412 --> 01:19:09,214
[Makofi]

1380
01:19:09,249 --> 01:19:10,413
-Hivyo basi, mambo matatu:

1381
01:19:10,448 --> 01:19:12,250
iPod ya skrini pana yenye vidhibiti vya kugusa,

1382
01:19:14,386 --> 01:19:18,828
simu ya mkononi ya kimapinduzi,

1383
01:19:18,863 --> 01:19:21,325
na kifaa cha mawasiliano ya mtandao cha uvumbuzi mkuu.

1384
01:19:21,360 --> 01:19:24,163
iPod, simu,

1385
01:19:24,198 --> 01:19:26,264
na kifaa cha mawasiliano ya mtandao.

1386
01:19:26,299 --> 01:19:29,905
iPod...

1387
01:19:29,940 --> 01:19:34,338
Simu...

1388
01:19:34,373 --> 01:19:37,979
Mnaanza kuelewa?

1389
01:19:38,014 --> 01:19:40,146
[Vigelegele na makofi]

1390
01:19:40,181 --> 01:19:42,511
Hivi si vifaa vitatu tofauti.

1391
01:19:42,546 --> 01:19:45,052
Hiki ni kifaa kimoja.

1392
01:19:45,087 --> 01:19:48,055
[Vigelegele na makofi]

1393
01:19:48,090 --> 01:19:52,356
Na tunakiita...

1394
01:19:52,391 --> 01:19:54,028
iPhone.

1395
01:19:54,063 --> 01:19:58,230
[Vigelegele na makofi]

1396
01:19:58,265 --> 01:20:00,595
Hapa kuna simu janja nne, sivyo?

1397
01:20:00,630 --> 01:20:02,465
Motorola Q, BlackBerry, Palm Treo,

1398
01:20:02,500 --> 01:20:05,237
Nokia E62 -- washukiwa wa kawaida.

1399
01:20:05,272 --> 01:20:07,173
Zote zina vibonyezo hivi ambavyo vipo hapo,

1400
01:20:07,208 --> 01:20:10,440
iwe unavihitaji au huvihitaji viwepo.

1401
01:20:10,475 --> 01:20:12,948
Na zote zina vitufe hivi vya kudhibiti

1402
01:20:12,983 --> 01:20:15,082
vilivyofungwa kwenye plastiki. -Kwa nini mtu yeyote

1403
01:20:15,117 --> 01:20:17,414
atake simu isiyo na vibonyezo?

1404
01:20:17,449 --> 01:20:19,515
-Sawa, tutakachofanya ni kuondoa vitufe hivi vyote

1405
01:20:19,550 --> 01:20:22,056
na kutengeneza kioo kikubwa tu.

1406
01:20:22,091 --> 01:20:23,959
Kioo kikubwa mno.

1407
01:20:23,994 --> 01:20:27,523
Na tutapoanza kusambaza mwezi wa Juni,

1408
01:20:27,558 --> 01:20:29,899
tutakuwa tukiuza iPhone kupitia maduka yetu wenyewe

1409
01:20:29,934 --> 01:20:32,330
na kupitia maduka ya Cingular. Na ni furaha yangu

1410
01:20:32,365 --> 01:20:34,068
kumtambulisha Mkurugenzi Mtendaji wa Cingular,

1411
01:20:34,103 --> 01:20:36,466
Stan Sigman.

1412
01:20:36,501 --> 01:20:40,437
-Hivi unanifanyia mzaha? -Nini?

1413
01:20:40,472 --> 01:20:43,539
-Huyo ni Stan Sigman. Huyo ni Mkurugenzi Mtendaji wa ATandT.

1414
01:20:43,574 --> 01:20:46,278
-Unajua, mimi na Steve tulikutana mara ya kwanza takriban miaka miwili iliyopita

1415
01:20:46,313 --> 01:20:49,314
katika Jiji la New York aliponishirikisha

1416
01:20:49,349 --> 01:20:52,647
maono haya aliyokuwa nayo kwa bidhaa hii.

1417
01:20:52,682 --> 01:20:56,090
-Huyu jamaa kweli. -Na tumekuwa tukiifanyia kazi

1418
01:20:56,125 --> 01:20:58,290
kwa muda mrefu na kwa kweli --- Haya jamani, inatosha.

1419
01:20:58,325 --> 01:21:01,095
Muda wa mchezo umeisha. Rudini kazini.

1420
01:21:01,130 --> 01:21:03,295
Nahitaji kielelezo cha awali cha Bold mkononi mwangu kufikia Ijumaa

1421
01:21:03,330 --> 01:21:06,232
chenye sehemu ya kutelezea inayofanya kazi.

1422
01:21:06,267 --> 01:21:08,465
Asanteni.

1423
01:21:08,500 --> 01:21:13,008
-Hilo ni jambo la kushangaza.

1424
01:21:13,043 --> 01:21:15,978
[Simu inaita]

1425
01:21:16,013 --> 01:21:17,947
Halo.

1426
01:21:22,151 --> 01:21:23,986
<i>-Habari. Je, huyu ni Douglas?</i>
-Ndiyo, ndiyo.

1427
01:21:24,021 --> 01:21:28,518
<i>-Ninatoka Tume ya Dhamana</i>
<i>na Kubadilishana Hisa,</i>

1428
01:21:28,553 --> 01:21:30,025
<i>na nilikuwa nikijiuliza ikiwa</i>
<i>unaweza kujibu maswali kadhaa</i>

1429
01:21:30,060 --> 01:21:33,424
<i>kwa ajili yangu.</i>
-Sawa. Bila shaka. Sikiliza huo mlio wa injini.

1430
01:21:33,459 --> 01:21:35,624
<i>-Je, ulihusika katika</i>
<i>umuajiri wa Bwana Paul Stanos?</i>

1431
01:21:35,659 --> 01:21:38,561
-Samahani. Unatoka wapi?

1432
01:21:38,596 --> 01:21:41,531
<i>-Ninatoka Tume ya Dhamana.</i>

1433
01:21:41,566 --> 01:21:46,272
-Je, hii ni simu ya dhati?

1434
01:21:48,177 --> 01:21:49,539
<i>-Ndiyo.</i>

1435
01:21:49,574 --> 01:21:52,245
-Ndiyo.
Umempigia simu mtu asiyehusika.

1436
01:21:52,280 --> 01:21:53,983
Siwezi kukusaidia
kwa jambo lolote kama hilo.

1437
01:21:54,018 --> 01:21:56,711
<i>-Je, huyu ni Douglas Fregin?</i>

1438
01:21:56,746 --> 01:21:58,152
-Ndiyo, bibi.
<i>-Samahani, hapa nimekuorodhesha</i>

1439
01:21:58,187 --> 01:22:00,154
<i>kama mmoja wa waanzilishi</i>
<i>wa kampuni hii.</i>

1440
01:22:00,189 --> 01:22:02,222
-Mimi... Ndiyo, nadhani mimi siye.
Ah...

1441
01:22:02,257 --> 01:22:05,324
-Doug?

1442
01:22:05,359 --> 01:22:09,130
-Lazima niondoke.

1443
01:22:09,165 --> 01:22:12,232
♪♪

1444
01:22:12,267 --> 01:22:14,102
[Mlio wa simu unalia]
-Samahani.

1445
01:22:14,137 --> 01:22:16,038
Namba ngeni?
-Hapana.

1446
01:22:16,073 --> 01:22:23,309
-Bwana Balsillie?
-Ndiyo.

1447
01:22:23,344 --> 01:22:26,510
-Karibu kwenye Ligi ya Taifa ya Hoki.

1448
01:22:26,545 --> 01:22:30,052
-Ahsante kwa kunikaribisha.

1449
01:22:35,323 --> 01:22:38,225
-Nimefurahi kukutana nawe.
Pita huku.

1450
01:22:38,260 --> 01:22:40,656
-Sawa, vyema.

1451
01:22:40,691 --> 01:22:42,427
-Hapa ndani.

1452
01:22:42,462 --> 01:22:44,033
-Ndiyo. Nimefurahi kukuona.
Ahsante kwa kutenga muda wako.

1453
01:22:44,068 --> 01:22:45,628
-Lo, kila mara nina muda
kwa ajili yako, Gary.

1454
01:22:48,765 --> 01:22:50,534
Nikutanishie kwa simu
na Copps Coliseum.

1455
01:22:53,704 --> 01:22:57,244
-Ipo katika uwanja wa michezo
kule Hamilton.

1456
01:22:57,279 --> 01:22:59,444
-Ndiyo. Waambie
nataka kuununua.

1457
01:23:02,284 --> 01:23:05,615
-Sawa. Nilidhani ulikuwa
unawanunua Pittsburgh Penguins.

1458
01:23:05,650 --> 01:23:08,156
-Ndiyo, nafanya hivyo. Twendeni.

1459
01:23:08,191 --> 01:23:10,422
-Sawa, inatupasa kuondoka.
-Subiri kidogo.

1460
01:23:12,723 --> 01:23:16,362
Hii ndiyo yenyewe.
Hii inatosha kabisa.

1461
01:23:18,399 --> 01:23:21,235
Hii ni nzuri.
-Hii inatosha kabisa?

1462
01:23:26,242 --> 01:23:28,836
-Apple wanazindua
soko la programu.

1463
01:23:28,871 --> 01:23:30,310
Watakuwepo
waendelezaji wa nje.

1464
01:23:30,345 --> 01:23:31,839
Yeyote -- yeyote -- yeyote -- mtu yeyote --

1465
01:23:31,874 --> 01:23:34,644
-Hali ni mbaya.
Wakati mbaya, wakati mbaya, wakati mbaya.

1466
01:23:34,679 --> 01:23:36,679
-Wakati mbaya.
-Waendelezaji wa nje.

1467
01:23:36,714 --> 01:23:38,285
-Hujambo, bwana.
-Ndiyo.

1468
01:23:38,320 --> 01:23:40,848
-Inakwama sana.
-Inatosha hivi hivi.

1469
01:23:40,883 --> 01:23:43,620
Inatosha hivi hivi.
-Sawa, sasa.

1470
01:23:43,655 --> 01:23:46,260
-Ndiyo, tumeipata.
-Doug, tafadhali.

1471
01:23:46,295 --> 01:23:48,163
Wanazindua
soko la programu.

1472
01:23:48,198 --> 01:23:49,692
-Sawa.
Kwa hiyo sehemu ya kugusa inafanya kazi.

1473
01:23:49,727 --> 01:23:52,794
Sijui kama naweza kusema kwamba inafanya kazi kwelikweli.

1474
01:23:52,829 --> 01:23:56,831
♪♪

1475
01:23:56,866 --> 01:24:00,406
-[Anashusha pumzi]

1476
01:24:00,441 --> 01:24:05,444
♪♪

1477
01:24:05,479 --> 01:24:09,382
-Nini?

1478
01:24:09,417 --> 01:24:11,186
-Je, una suti?

1479
01:24:11,221 --> 01:24:16,686
♪♪

1480
01:24:16,721 --> 01:24:19,194
-Inchi mbili nukta nne, kioo cha HVGA cha mia nne themanini kwa mia tatu sitini,

1481
01:24:19,229 --> 01:24:20,888
na cha juu zaidi ya yote,

1482
01:24:20,923 --> 01:24:29,567
kifaa cha kwanza duniani cha mguso-elekezi, ambacho tunaamini kitakuwa

1483
01:24:29,602 --> 01:24:34,638
kifaa kikuu cha uongozi kwa vifaa vyote vya mkononi

1484
01:24:34,673 --> 01:24:36,772
ndani ya miaka miwili ijayo.

1485
01:24:36,807 --> 01:24:42,184
BlackBerry Bold.

1486
01:24:42,219 --> 01:24:45,220
-Ni hayo tu?

1487
01:24:45,255 --> 01:24:48,355
-Ndiyo.

1488
01:24:48,390 --> 01:24:50,324
-Hicho -- hicho ndicho mlichotuletea?

1489
01:24:52,889 --> 01:24:55,791
Mguso-elekezi?

1490
01:24:55,826 --> 01:24:57,727
-Ee...

1491
01:24:57,762 --> 01:25:01,203
-M-meona kile kitu cha Apple?

1492
01:25:01,238 --> 01:25:02,666
Maoni yoyote kuhusu hilo? -Mengi sana. Ndiyo.

1493
01:25:02,701 --> 01:25:06,505
Ni kichezeo kilichoundwa kupita kiasi, kinachojaribu kufanya mambo mengi mno

1494
01:25:06,540 --> 01:25:09,673
ambacho kitakwamisha mtandao wowote utakaokuwa rahisi kuhadaika na kuukubali.

1495
01:25:13,778 --> 01:25:16,482
Ni, kwa kila kipimo,

1496
01:25:16,517 --> 01:25:18,484
kinyume kabisa cha kila kitu tunachofanya hapa Research in Motion.

1497
01:25:18,519 --> 01:25:22,422
Data kidogo, bila nakshi nyingi, mtandao wa kuaminika.

1498
01:25:22,457 --> 01:25:24,655
Sawa, hiyo ndiyo BlackBerry.

1499
01:25:24,690 --> 01:25:28,560
-Kaulimbiu ya kuvutia, Mike.

1500
01:25:28,595 --> 01:25:32,960
-Kwa hiyo, nadhani unataka tu
kuharibu mtandao wako wote?

1501
01:25:32,995 --> 01:25:35,270
Kwa sababu ndivyo itakavyofanya.

1502
01:25:35,305 --> 01:25:37,965
-Ndiyo. Kwenye iPhone, wameweka
kibodi moja kwa moja kwenye kioo.

1503
01:25:38,000 --> 01:25:40,374
-Na ni jambo la kijinga zaidi
ambalo sijawahi kuona

1504
01:25:40,409 --> 01:25:42,772
katika maisha yangu yote.

1505
01:25:42,807 --> 01:25:46,644
Muulize yeyote anachokipenda zaidi
kuhusu BlackBerry yake

1506
01:25:46,679 --> 01:25:48,910
na utapata jibu lile lile
kila wakati:

1507
01:25:48,945 --> 01:25:50,714
Kibodi na mlio wa kubonyeza.
Sawa

1508
01:25:50,749 --> 01:25:53,684
H-hiki --
-Vema...

1509
01:25:53,719 --> 01:25:55,917
Ndiyo, ndiyo.
-Soko hili lote

1510
01:25:55,952 --> 01:25:59,822
lilitokana
na ubunifu wetu,

1511
01:25:59,857 --> 01:26:02,264
wazo letu la kuweka kibodi
kwenye simu.

1512
01:26:02,299 --> 01:26:04,827
Tulifanya hivyo. Tulijenga jambo hilo
kutokana na lundo la takataka mwaka wa 1996.

1513
01:26:04,862 --> 01:26:06,532
-Hiyo ni kaulimbiu nyingine basi

1514
01:26:06,567 --> 01:26:09,601
Sijui, Mike.

1515
01:26:09,636 --> 01:26:13,803
Kampuni ya AT&T ina Apple,
tulikuwa tunatumaini

1516
01:26:13,838 --> 01:26:16,311
ungekuja hapa
na kiangamizi cha iPhone.

1517
01:26:16,346 --> 01:26:17,906
-Mimi --
sihitaji kuiangamiza

1518
01:26:17,941 --> 01:26:22,482
kwa sababu itajiangamiza yenyewe

1519
01:26:22,517 --> 01:26:24,550
na itauangusha
mtandao mzima wa hovyo wa

1520
01:26:24,585 --> 01:26:27,520
Cingular pamoja nayo.

1521
01:26:27,555 --> 01:26:29,016
Nawapa kitu cha thamani kama dhahabu,

1522
01:26:29,051 --> 01:26:30,919
na nadhani ninyi nyote
hamuielewi.

1523
01:26:30,954 --> 01:26:33,460
Eeh...

1524
01:26:33,495 --> 01:26:35,462
Niliunda aina hii nzima ya bidhaa.

1525
01:26:35,497 --> 01:26:37,464
Niliunda soko hili lote kabisa.

1526
01:26:37,499 --> 01:26:40,434
Niliunda aina hii nzima ya bidhaa.

1527
01:26:40,469 --> 01:26:44,438
Basi nisikilizeni -- kiguso hiki ni kama pedi ya kipanya.

1528
01:26:44,473 --> 01:26:48,871
Ee --

1529
01:26:52,382 --> 01:26:55,383
Iliyoundwa ndani ya simu.

1530
01:26:55,418 --> 01:27:00,454
-Ndiyo.

1531
01:27:00,489 --> 01:27:02,324
Na... Sawa. Haya.

1532
01:27:02,359 --> 01:27:04,392
Ndiyo. Sawa. Inatosha.

1533
01:27:06,363 --> 01:27:07,923
Asanteni, jamani, kwa kuja hapa. Hebu fanyeni hivi.

1534
01:27:10,730 --> 01:27:15,766
Hebu tu -- tutazungumzia jambo hili ndani ya kampuni yetu.

1535
01:27:15,801 --> 01:27:19,704
Tutawasiliana nanyi tena, sawa?

1536
01:27:19,739 --> 01:27:21,871
Mwambieni Jim kuwa tulimkosa.

1537
01:27:21,906 --> 01:27:24,544
-Twendeni.

1538
01:27:24,579 --> 01:27:26,678
-Amerudi. Yuko Waterloo, anafanya kazi kwa sababu...

1539
01:27:26,713 --> 01:27:28,911
Hivyo basi, alinitaka niahidi nisitaje...

1540
01:27:33,489 --> 01:27:35,522
lile jambo jingine.

1541
01:27:40,397 --> 01:27:45,664
Bado hatujafika huko kabisa.

1542
01:27:45,699 --> 01:27:48,931
Lakini tunatengeneza kitu cha siri sana.

1543
01:27:48,966 --> 01:27:51,637
Aliniambia niahidi nisizungumzie jambo hilo, ee..

1544
01:27:51,672 --> 01:27:54,772
Kuhusu mfano wa awali, bado tuna wiki chache, ee,

1545
01:27:54,807 --> 01:27:59,645
lakini, unajua,

1546
01:27:59,680 --> 01:28:02,648
Ninaweza kuonyesha kielelezo chake kwa kutumia mfano wetu wa Bold.

1547
01:28:04,388 --> 01:28:06,751
Hivyo bado ni BlackBerry.

1548
01:28:06,786 --> 01:28:09,688
Hii ni BlackBerry yetu. Kwa hiyo wewe --

1549
01:28:09,723 --> 01:28:13,527
Isipokuwa pale -- pale tulipoweka vibonyezo hapa,

1550
01:28:16,763 --> 01:28:18,730
eeh, kioo, sehemu yote ni kioo, isipokuwa yetu,

1551
01:28:18,765 --> 01:28:20,699
unapoibonyeza, utapata ule mlio wa kuridhisha,

1552
01:28:20,734 --> 01:28:22,932
ule mlio wa BlackBerry, mlio wetu wa kipekee.

1553
01:28:22,967 --> 01:28:29,807
Hivyo, kioo, vibonyezo, simu.

1554
01:28:29,842 --> 01:28:35,450
Kioo, vibonyezo, simu.

1555
01:28:35,485 --> 01:28:38,816
Kioo, vibonyezo, simu.

1556
01:28:38,851 --> 01:28:43,821
Je, unaelewa?

1557
01:28:43,856 --> 01:28:47,121
♪♪

1558
01:28:48,157 --> 01:28:52,500
♪♪

1559
01:28:52,535 --> 01:28:54,931
♪♪

1560
01:28:54,966 --> 01:29:00,167
-Mike. Mike? Ni nini hicho ulichofanya, bwana!

1561
01:29:00,202 --> 01:29:05,612
-Liko wapi lile gari la kifahari?

1562
01:29:05,647 --> 01:29:10,848
-Uwezo wa juu ni watu elfu kumi na saba, lakini tunaweza kuuongeza

1563
01:29:10,883 --> 01:29:14,049
hadi elfu kumi na tisa bila matatizo mengi.

1564
01:29:14,084 --> 01:29:15,853
-Haya. Nataka mambo haya yote ya mpira wa kikapu yaondoke.

1565
01:29:15,888 --> 01:29:18,625
Kuanzia sasa, sehemu hii itakuwa uwanja wa kudumu wa kuteleza kwenye barafu.

1566
01:29:18,660 --> 01:29:20,693
-[Anaguna]

1567
01:29:20,728 --> 01:29:22,662
Hatuwezi kufanya hivyo. -Kwa nini?

1568
01:29:22,697 --> 01:29:25,830
-Tuna mikataba hai na wateja kumi na wawili.

1569
01:29:25,865 --> 01:29:28,734
-Ifute yote. -Sawa, lakini kutakuwa na --

1570
01:29:28,769 --> 01:29:31,704
-Nitalipa faini zote.

1571
01:29:31,739 --> 01:29:33,134
Nataka kile kiwe chumba changu binafsi cha kutazamia.

1572
01:29:33,169 --> 01:29:35,576
-Kile si chumba cha kutazamia.

1573
01:29:35,611 --> 01:29:37,039
Hicho siyo kisanduku.

1574
01:29:37,074 --> 01:29:41,142
-Hapana, hapana, hapana.

1575
01:29:41,177 --> 01:29:42,946
Sawa, kwa hiyo ni kioo,

1576
01:29:46,182 --> 01:29:47,918
lakini kinahitaji bawaba iliyoinuka
au kiamshio,

1577
01:29:47,953 --> 01:29:49,183
kama nilivyoandika, kati yake
na kiwiliwili

1578
01:29:49,218 --> 01:29:51,691
ili kifaa kizima kitoe mlio wa mbofyo
unapokibonyeza.

1579
01:29:51,726 --> 01:29:54,628
-[Ananong'ona]

1580
01:29:54,663 --> 01:29:56,630
-Subiri. Nini?

1581
01:29:56,665 --> 01:29:59,864
-Ninajiuliza tu kwa nini
tunataka kufanya hivyo.

1582
01:29:59,899 --> 01:30:02,031
-Hilo -- hilo -- hilo --
siyo swali

1583
01:30:02,066 --> 01:30:03,835
unaloniuliza hapa.
Sielewi --

1584
01:30:06,202 --> 01:30:08,807
"Kwa nini" haijalishi kwako?
Sawa?

1585
01:30:08,842 --> 01:30:11,106
Kwa sababu nimesema hivyo.

1586
01:30:11,141 --> 01:30:13,647
Kwa sababu hicho ndicho nilichouza.
Sawa?

1587
01:30:13,682 --> 01:30:16,210
Wewe ni nani, kwani?

1588
01:30:16,245 --> 01:30:18,014
-Tulia, Mike.

1589
01:30:18,049 --> 01:30:20,852
[Mlio wa simu unalia]
-Jamani, tafadhali.

1590
01:30:20,887 --> 01:30:23,151
Hali ya kimya!
Tunapokuwa ofisini.

1591
01:30:23,186 --> 01:30:25,659
Charles!

1592
01:30:25,694 --> 01:30:28,530
-Zimeni simu.
-Samahani. Samahani, Mike.

1593
01:30:28,565 --> 01:30:30,796
Samahani kila mtu.

1594
01:30:30,831 --> 01:30:32,534
-Sawa, kwa hiyo unajua ninachofikiri
haya yote ni nini,

1595
01:30:32,569 --> 01:30:34,800
ni kwamba tunajaribu kuleta ule mbofyo
wa zamani wa BlackBerry

1596
01:30:34,835 --> 01:30:35,768
huku tukichukua mfumo wa
kioo kipya cha iPhone.

1597
01:30:37,805 --> 01:30:40,201
Hivyo tu.
-Hapana, hapana, hapana.

1598
01:30:40,236 --> 01:30:44,238
Hatutaki kukubali
kitu chochote kinachohusiana na Apple!

1599
01:30:44,273 --> 01:30:47,516
Jamani!

1600
01:30:47,551 --> 01:30:48,946
Si jambo gumu hata kidogo.

1601
01:30:48,981 --> 01:30:52,719
Sawa? Tunawalipa pesa nyingi sana.

1602
01:30:52,754 --> 01:30:56,217
Hili si jambo gumu hata kidogo.

1603
01:30:56,252 --> 01:30:58,120
Ni baobonye kwenye kioo,

1604
01:30:58,155 --> 01:31:00,859
kwenye baobonye.

1605
01:31:00,894 --> 01:31:02,663
♪♪

1606
01:31:02,698 --> 01:31:06,095
Na sijali
unachofikiria kuhusu hilo.

1607
01:31:06,130 --> 01:31:07,932
-Mike.

1608
01:31:07,967 --> 01:31:12,640
♪♪

1609
01:31:12,675 --> 01:31:14,675
♪♪

1610
01:31:14,710 --> 01:31:17,007
Doug anazungumza nini hapa.

1611
01:31:17,042 --> 01:31:22,782
Kukubali kile Apple wanachofanya?

1612
01:31:22,817 --> 01:31:28,590
Sielewi.

1613
01:31:28,625 --> 01:31:29,723
-Umerudi kutoka New York

1614
01:31:29,758 --> 01:31:31,252
ukizungumzia
simu mpya kabisa, sivyo?

1615
01:31:31,287 --> 01:31:32,759
Sampuli ya awali ndani ya wiki moja.
Tunafanya nini hapa?

1616
01:31:32,794 --> 01:31:34,024
-Naweza kuzungumza nawe?
-Ni sampuli ya awali,

1617
01:31:34,059 --> 01:31:35,663
Charles, naweza kutengeneza
kifaa hiki mimi mwenyewe

1618
01:31:35,698 --> 01:31:38,699
ndani ya usiku mmoja nikihitaji.
-Bado tunapaswa kusafirisha

1619
01:31:38,734 --> 01:31:40,030
kifaa hiki.
-Nilisema tumia Onyx --

1620
01:31:40,065 --> 01:31:41,669
-Nilifanya hivyo! Kwenye mzingo!

1621
01:31:41,704 --> 01:31:43,803
♪♪

1622
01:31:43,838 --> 01:31:46,135
Haya basi, China.

1623
01:31:46,170 --> 01:31:49,611
Hii ndiyo njia pekee ya kukamilisha hili.

1624
01:31:49,646 --> 01:31:56,013
Samahani, China.

1625
01:31:56,048 --> 01:31:59,621
♪♪

1626
01:31:59,656 --> 01:32:01,249
♪♪

1627
01:32:01,284 --> 01:32:04,318
-Ndiyo. Potelea mbali. Lifanye.

1628
01:32:04,353 --> 01:32:09,598
China.

1629
01:32:09,633 --> 01:32:14,636
China. Tulifanye.
-Subiri. Hapana, hapana.

1630
01:32:14,671 --> 01:32:18,607
Hakumaanishi hivyo.
-Haya, haya, haya. Usi—

1631
01:32:18,642 --> 01:32:20,334
Usinisemee.
-Lakini, Mike, unafanya nini?

1632
01:32:20,369 --> 01:32:21,973
-Nafanya nini? Najaribu kumbakiza mteja wetu

1633
01:32:22,008 --> 01:32:23,975
mkubwa kabisa, wewe unafanya nini?

1634
01:32:24,010 --> 01:32:26,109
-Mike, najaribu kukusaidia.
-Lakini husaidii hata hivyo.

1635
01:32:26,144 --> 01:32:28,276
Husaidii.
Hunisaidii.

1636
01:32:28,311 --> 01:32:30,685
Hili halinisaidii.

1637
01:32:33,349 --> 01:32:35,118
Kama ungeweza kunisaidia,
tusingekuwa hapa.

1638
01:32:35,153 --> 01:32:36,691
Sihitaji msaada wako tena, sawa?

1639
01:32:36,726 --> 01:32:38,022
Wewe huna msaada wowote!

1640
01:32:38,057 --> 01:32:39,793
-Sawa.

1641
01:32:39,828 --> 01:32:42,631
-Tafuta namna ya kuitatua China

1642
01:32:42,666 --> 01:32:44,259
Tafuta namna ya kuitatua China.

1643
01:32:52,302 --> 01:32:54,104
Na nitakitengeneza kitu hiki mimi mwenyewe.

1644
01:33:04,413 --> 01:33:06,215
♪♪

1645
01:33:14,258 --> 01:33:16,027
♪♪

1646
01:33:17,866 --> 01:33:20,229
♪♪

1647
01:33:30,109 --> 01:33:37,048
Laana.
[Simu inalia]

1648
01:33:37,083 --> 01:33:43,989
Nini?
<i>-Je, huyu ni Mike Lazaridis?</i>

1649
01:33:44,024 --> 01:33:50,963
-Nani -- Huyu ni nani?
<i>-Jina langu ni Dara Frankel.</i>

1650
01:33:50,998 --> 01:33:53,295
<i>Ninatoka Tume ya Dhamana na Fedha.</i>
<i>Una muda kidogo?</i>

1651
01:33:53,330 --> 01:33:55,737
-Siyo kweli. Siyo sasa hivi.
Hii inahusu nini?

1652
01:33:55,772 --> 01:33:58,300
<i>-Najaribu kufuatilia</i>
<i>taarifa fulani</i>

1653
01:33:58,335 --> 01:34:01,138
<i>kuhusu hisa fulani</i>
<i>ambazo kampuni yako ilitoa.</i>

1654
01:34:01,173 --> 01:34:04,240
-Kwa kweli, hiyo siyo -- nisingejua
lolote kuhusu hilo.

1655
01:34:04,275 --> 01:34:05,945
Nadhani ungetaka
kuongea na Jim.

1656
01:34:05,980 --> 01:34:08,442
<i>-Sawa.</i>
<i>Je, kuna muda mzuri</i>

1657
01:34:08,477 --> 01:34:11,852
<i>wa kuja na kuongelea jambo hili?</i>

1658
01:34:11,887 --> 01:34:15,185
-Hapana, sidhani -- hapana.

1659
01:34:15,220 --> 01:34:18,727
-Sawa. Nimefika.

1660
01:34:18,762 --> 01:34:21,356
Nimefika. Nimefika. Nimefika.

1661
01:34:21,391 --> 01:34:23,325
-Jack Manishen anasema
anahitaji kukuona.

1662
01:34:26,066 --> 01:34:27,736
-Sawa. Ndiyo. Yuko wapi?

1663
01:34:27,771 --> 01:34:29,067
-Amepiga kambi nje ya ofisi yako.
-Safi.

1664
01:34:29,102 --> 01:34:30,970
-Shell, nifanyie upendeleo.

1665
01:34:31,005 --> 01:34:32,807
Wasiliana na ofisi ya Carl Yankowski na umjulishe

1666
01:34:32,842 --> 01:34:36,778
kwamba Jim Balsillie ana tiketi za usiku wa ufunguzi

1667
01:34:40,542 --> 01:34:43,411
wa Hamilton Penguins kwa ajili yake.

1668
01:34:43,446 --> 01:34:45,919
Najua jinsi anavyopenda
mchezo wa hoki.

1669
01:34:45,954 --> 01:34:48,053
Haya, haya. Tulia.
Umenipata.

1670
01:34:48,088 --> 01:34:50,121
-Yule mwanamke yule yule kutoka Tume ya Dhamana na Fedha
anazidi kupiga simu.

1671
01:34:50,156 --> 01:34:53,025
Je, nimpate namba yako?
-Hapana.

1672
01:34:58,395 --> 01:35:00,362
-Sawa, basi robo ya kwanza,
robo ya pili, robo ya tatu.

1673
01:35:00,397 --> 01:35:02,430
Robo ya nne ya mwaka.

1674
01:35:02,465 --> 01:35:05,136
Na hapa ndipo tulipo.

1675
01:35:07,503 --> 01:35:17,115
[Mlio wa kubonyeza]

1676
01:35:19,218 --> 01:35:22,153
-Hizi ni takwimu za nani?

1677
01:35:22,188 --> 01:35:23,352
-Makadirio ya ndani ya kampuni ya Apple.

1678
01:35:23,387 --> 01:35:27,092
-Walitoa takwimu hizo
siku ya Ijumaa.

1679
01:35:27,127 --> 01:35:28,863
-Dola mia tano kwa ruzuku kamili?

1680
01:35:28,898 --> 01:35:30,260
Hii ndiyo simu ghali zaidi
duniani.

1681
01:35:30,295 --> 01:35:33,296
-Ina mvuto mkubwa zaidi kwa wateja

1682
01:35:33,331 --> 01:35:36,134
kuliko bidhaa yoyote katika historia.

1683
01:35:36,169 --> 01:35:38,939
Tutatoka kuwa simu namba moja duniani

1684
01:35:38,974 --> 01:35:39,907
na kuwa ile simu ambayo watu walikuwa nayo
kabla ya kununua iPhone.

1685
01:35:39,942 --> 01:35:41,469
[Muziki]

1686
01:35:41,504 --> 01:35:44,340
-Mambo yatakuwa sawa.
Mike atatafuta suluhu.

1687
01:35:44,375 --> 01:35:49,048
[Hodi mlangoni]

1688
01:35:49,083 --> 01:35:57,089
Nini?

1689
01:35:57,124 --> 01:36:00,521
[Hodi ya nguvu zaidi]

1690
01:36:00,556 --> 01:36:02,259
[Muziki]

1691
01:36:02,294 --> 01:36:04,327
-Habari, mmm...

1692
01:36:04,362 --> 01:36:07,297
Kwa nini mamlaka ya usimamizi wa fedha inatuchunguza?

1693
01:36:07,332 --> 01:36:12,170
-Walikupigia simu?

1694
01:36:12,205 --> 01:36:14,007
-Ndiyo. Jambo fulani --
Kuhusu chaguzi za hisa?

1695
01:36:16,638 --> 01:36:19,441
-Nina hakika si jambo kubwa. Ndiyo.

1696
01:36:19,476 --> 01:36:21,146
-Si -- Si jambo kubwa?

1697
01:36:21,181 --> 01:36:24,985
-Ndiyo. Kuna nini kuhusu hili
jambo la Apple?

1698
01:36:25,020 --> 01:36:27,119
-Nini--Inakuwaje kuhusu hilo?

1699
01:36:27,154 --> 01:36:29,550
-Je, tuna wasiwasi?
-Hapana.

1700
01:36:29,585 --> 01:36:32,388
-Sawa. Kwa nini?

1701
01:36:34,326 --> 01:36:36,128
-Kwa sababu kimoja chao
kinatumia kiwango cha mtandao

1702
01:36:36,163 --> 01:36:39,626
sawa na simu elfu tano za BlackBerry.

1703
01:36:39,661 --> 01:36:41,595
Kwa sababu haina kicharazio.
Kwa sababu kitu hicho ni mzaha.

1704
01:36:41,630 --> 01:36:43,399
-Sasa kwa nini watu wananiambia
kuwa wako karibu kutuangamiza?

1705
01:36:43,434 --> 01:36:45,203
-Kwa sababu ni wajinga.

1706
01:36:45,238 --> 01:36:48,041
-[Anashusha pumzi]

1707
01:36:50,375 --> 01:36:53,475
♪♪

1708
01:36:53,510 --> 01:36:55,983
-Nipangie mkutano
na Stan Sigman wa ATandT.

1709
01:37:08,162 --> 01:37:10,492
♪♪

1710
01:37:14,971 --> 01:37:20,205
-Unafanya nini?

1711
01:37:20,240 --> 01:37:23,604
[Milio]

1712
01:37:23,639 --> 01:37:31,216
<i>-Sawa, wakati wa mapema zaidi</i>
<i>ninaoweza kupata ni mwezi ujao.</i>

1713
01:37:31,251 --> 01:37:34,087
<i>Ofisi yake imesema</i>
<i>anaondoka kwenda likizo leo.</i>

1714
01:37:34,122 --> 01:37:35,649
-Mwambie nakuja
Atlanta sasa hivi.

1715
01:37:35,684 --> 01:37:37,684
♪♪

1716
01:37:37,719 --> 01:37:39,587
Twende. Twende!

1717
01:37:39,622 --> 01:37:42,689
Waambie tutafika huko
baada ya saa moja.

1718
01:37:42,724 --> 01:37:50,169
-Hujambo, ni --

1719
01:37:50,204 --> 01:37:52,303
♪♪

1720
01:37:52,338 --> 01:37:53,667
-Gary, habari yako?

1721
01:37:53,702 --> 01:37:56,241
<i>-Salama. Tuko tayari</i>
<i>kuanza hapa.</i>

1722
01:37:56,276 --> 01:37:58,705
<i>Ni haraka gani unaweza</i>
<i>kufika New York?</i>

1723
01:37:58,740 --> 01:38:00,707
-Vema, mm... Wakati wowote kesho.

1724
01:38:00,742 --> 01:38:02,313
<i>-Vipi kuhusu leo?</i>

1725
01:38:02,348 --> 01:38:04,612
-Hiyo inaweza kuwa ngumu kidogo kwangu.

1726
01:38:06,385 --> 01:38:09,485
<i>-Nina bodi hapa sasa, na sijui</i>

1727
01:38:09,520 --> 01:38:12,257
<i>-ni lini watakutana tena kwa pamoja.</i>

1728
01:38:12,292 --> 01:38:14,028
<i>-Ukitaka kusubiri, ni hiari yako.</i>

1729
01:38:14,063 --> 01:38:15,557
<i>-Ni mpango wako.</i>

1730
01:38:15,592 --> 01:38:17,427
-Ndiyo. Hapana, hiyo inafaa, Gary.

1731
01:38:17,462 --> 01:38:20,067
Nitakuwepo -- Ndiyo, nitakuwepo.

1732
01:38:20,102 --> 01:38:22,366
<i>-Natazamia kwa hamu.</i>

1733
01:38:22,401 --> 01:38:24,731
-Sawa. Vyema. Kwaheri.

1734
01:38:24,766 --> 01:38:27,041
♪♪

1735
01:38:27,076 --> 01:38:28,537
Mipango imebadilika.
Tunakwenda JFK.

1736
01:38:28,572 --> 01:38:30,374
-Tumeshajipanga.

1737
01:38:30,409 --> 01:38:32,442
-Nisikilize mimi, wewe mwenye domo!

1738
01:38:32,477 --> 01:38:35,478
Nikisema tunakwenda JFK,
tunakwenda JFK!

1739
01:38:35,513 --> 01:38:37,612
Umeelewa?

1740
01:38:37,647 --> 01:38:39,416
-Kwa hiyo--hatuonani na
Sigman, basi?

1741
01:38:39,451 --> 01:38:42,056
-Ninafanya kila kitu.

1742
01:38:42,091 --> 01:38:43,486
♪♪

1743
01:38:43,521 --> 01:38:46,258
♪♪

1744
01:38:46,293 --> 01:38:48,524
♪♪

1745
01:38:48,559 --> 01:38:55,531
♪♪

1746
01:38:55,566 --> 01:39:02,538
♪♪

1747
01:39:02,573 --> 01:39:09,545
♪♪

1748
01:39:09,580 --> 01:39:16,519
-Hee!

1749
01:39:16,554 --> 01:39:23,526
Laana.

1750
01:39:23,561 --> 01:39:26,331
[Anaugua]

1751
01:39:30,568 --> 01:39:32,205
-Jim yuko wapi?
-Sijui kabisa.

1752
01:39:32,240 --> 01:39:33,503
-Haya, tunatakiwa
tukuondoe hapa.

1753
01:39:33,538 --> 01:39:36,011
-Nini? Kwa nini?
-Mamlaka ya Soko la Hisa inatuvamia.

1754
01:39:38,345 --> 01:39:40,477
-Subiri, nini?

1755
01:39:40,512 --> 01:39:41,775
-Nipe simu yako.

1756
01:39:41,810 --> 01:39:43,315
-[Anashusha pumzi]
-Simu yako ya laana iko wapi?

1757
01:39:43,350 --> 01:39:44,514
[Gonga mlangoni]
-Mike Lazaridis?

1758
01:39:44,549 --> 01:39:45,779
-Unaweza kushughulikia hili?

1759
01:39:45,814 --> 01:39:48,518
Wewe ni nani?
-Tulizungumza kwenye simu.

1760
01:39:48,553 --> 01:39:50,652
Ungependa kuja na kujibu
maswali kadhaa?

1761
01:39:50,687 --> 01:39:53,523
-Sawa. Sawa.

1762
01:39:53,558 --> 01:39:56,163
Ni mimi mnayemtafuta, sivyo? Sawa.

1763
01:39:56,198 --> 01:39:58,396
-Sawa.

1764
01:40:02,303 --> 01:40:04,732
-Sawa, nini?
Wanafanya nini?

1765
01:40:08,243 --> 01:40:10,276
Hiyo ni -- Hiyo ni -- Hapana, hapana.

1766
01:40:11,873 --> 01:40:13,411
Hawawezi kugusa
kitu chochote kati ya hivyo.

1767
01:40:13,446 --> 01:40:14,775
Wao --

1768
01:40:14,810 --> 01:40:16,348
♪♪

1769
01:40:16,383 --> 01:40:17,844
♪♪

1770
01:40:17,879 --> 01:40:20,088
-Nywila kwenye kila kitu.
-Lo!

1771
01:40:20,123 --> 01:40:28,162
Nywila ni nini, Mike?

1772
01:40:28,197 --> 01:40:36,236
-Je, ninalazimika
kukupa hiyo?

1773
01:40:36,271 --> 01:40:38,403
-Hapana.

1774
01:40:38,438 --> 01:40:41,604
Je, unaficha kitu?

1775
01:40:41,639 --> 01:40:45,377
-Eeeh...

1776
01:40:45,412 --> 01:40:46,576
Je, sipaswi kuwa na mwanasheria au mtu kama huyo kwa ajili ya jambo hili?

1777
01:40:46,611 --> 01:40:50,283
-Je, unadhani unamhitaji mwanasheria?

1778
01:40:50,318 --> 01:40:51,878
♪♪

1779
01:40:51,913 --> 01:40:56,388
♪♪

1780
01:40:56,423 --> 01:40:58,489
-Jim.

1781
01:40:58,524 --> 01:41:06,398
♪♪

1782
01:41:06,433 --> 01:41:14,274
♪♪

1783
01:41:14,309 --> 01:41:16,309
-Gary, nini kinaendelea?

1784
01:41:16,344 --> 01:41:22,645
Umenifanya -- umenifanya nisubiri hapa nje.

1785
01:41:22,680 --> 01:41:29,190
-Jim, sikiliza, hatutapoteza muda wako hapa, sawa?

1786
01:41:29,225 --> 01:41:30,422
Haitatokea kati yako na timu ya Penguins.

1787
01:41:30,457 --> 01:41:32,490
-Nini?

1788
01:41:32,525 --> 01:41:34,591
-Tumepiga kura na wamiliki wengine na kwa bahati mbaya,

1789
01:41:34,626 --> 01:41:38,496
kura zimekuwa kinyume chako, ishirini na sita kwa sifuri.

1790
01:41:38,531 --> 01:41:40,234
-Subiri kwanza. Subiri, subiri.

1791
01:41:40,269 --> 01:41:42,566
Nilidhani tulikuwa na makubaliano.

1792
01:41:42,601 --> 01:41:45,470
Lini wamiliki wengine walipata hata fursa ya...?

1793
01:41:45,505 --> 01:41:47,406
Samahani. Nini kimebadilika hapa, rafiki yangu?

1794
01:41:47,441 --> 01:41:50,244
-Wamiliki hawakuona kuwa wewe

1795
01:41:50,279 --> 01:41:52,642
ni mtu mwenye tabia njema na uadilifu.

1796
01:41:52,677 --> 01:41:55,249
-Sijui hata jambo hilo lina maana gani.

1797
01:41:55,284 --> 01:41:56,547
Gary, ni upuuzi gani huu?

1798
01:41:56,582 --> 01:42:00,848
-Unajua, inachekesha.

1799
01:42:00,883 --> 01:42:04,588
Ni jambo moja kuwa na mpango wa siri

1800
01:42:04,623 --> 01:42:07,954
wa kuihujumu Ligi ya Kitaifa ya Magongo na kuhamishia timu nchini Kanada.

1801
01:42:07,989 --> 01:42:09,593
Ni jambo jingine kabisa kujivuna

1802
01:42:09,628 --> 01:42:11,232
mbele ya marafiki zako matajiri kabla hata hujafanya hivyo.

1803
01:42:11,267 --> 01:42:13,828
-[Anaguna]

1804
01:42:13,863 --> 01:42:15,566
-Lo, ninyi ni wajinga kupindukia.

1805
01:42:15,601 --> 01:42:19,405
Unajua nini? Labda nitaishika na kuinunua ligi hii nzima.

1806
01:42:19,440 --> 01:42:22,342
Eti? Unaonaje hilo?

1807
01:42:29,318 --> 01:42:32,319
-Don, unaweza kuhakikisha Bwana Balsillie

1808
01:42:35,258 --> 01:42:38,556
anafika salama nchini Kanada?

1809
01:42:38,591 --> 01:42:39,821
-Lo, potelea mbali ninyi watu!

1810
01:42:39,856 --> 01:42:41,790
Koma kabisa!

1811
01:42:41,825 --> 01:42:43,462
Jiandaeni kwa unyakuzi wa kinguvu

1812
01:42:43,497 --> 01:42:46,729
wa ligi hii nzima, sawa, wewe mpumbavu?

1813
01:42:46,764 --> 01:42:50,238
Unadhani sitafanya hivyo kweli?

1814
01:42:50,273 --> 01:42:51,899
Ninatokea Waterloo, mahali ambapo mivampaya huonekana!

1815
01:42:51,934 --> 01:42:55,672
♪♪

1816
01:42:55,707 --> 01:42:57,905
Nenda, nenda, nenda, nenda, nenda!

1817
01:42:57,940 --> 01:43:03,581
-Hatutawahi kufika.
-Nimesema twende!

1818
01:43:03,616 --> 01:43:08,916
-Mcheleweshe Sigman.
-Nilipiga simu.

1819
01:43:08,951 --> 01:43:10,522
Walisema kuwa ameshaondoka kwa ajili ya likizo?

1820
01:43:10,557 --> 01:43:15,329
-Wapi?

1821
01:43:15,364 --> 01:43:16,693
-Walisema tu kuwa anaenda uwanja wa ndege.

1822
01:43:16,728 --> 01:43:17,859
-Vizuri, nasi pia tunaenda huko.

1823
01:43:17,894 --> 01:43:19,432
[Mngurumo wa injini ya ndege]

1824
01:43:19,467 --> 01:43:20,928
♪♪

1825
01:43:20,963 --> 01:43:22,732
-Na hii ni sahihi yako?

1826
01:43:22,767 --> 01:43:24,668
-Ndiyo.

1827
01:43:24,703 --> 01:43:31,279
-Na hii?

1828
01:43:31,314 --> 01:43:34,777
Sijui
unachokitafuta.

1829
01:43:34,812 --> 01:43:37,615
Hizi ni mikataba ya kawaida
ya ajira.

1830
01:43:41,555 --> 01:43:42,851
-Ninajiuliza tu jinsi ulivyoweza kuwashawishi wahandisi hawa wote

1831
01:43:42,886 --> 01:43:44,457
kutoka kote duniani
kuja mpaka huku Kanada.

1832
01:43:44,492 --> 01:43:47,691
Haliingii akilini.

1833
01:43:47,726 --> 01:43:51,893
-Ni kwa sababu wanapata nafasi ya kufanyia kazi
simu bora zaidi duniani.

1834
01:43:51,928 --> 01:43:54,962
-Mike.
-Eeh?

1835
01:43:54,997 --> 01:43:57,701
-Kila mmoja wa mikataba hii
unatoa fursa ya hisa zenye tarehe ya zamani.

1836
01:43:57,736 --> 01:44:01,771
Ulikuwa ukipanga bei ya hisa zako kinyume cha sheria

1837
01:44:01,806 --> 01:44:03,575
ili uweze kuajiri wahandisi
kwa pesa ambazo hukuwa nazo.

1838
01:44:03,610 --> 01:44:07,579
Je, unajua adhabu yake ni nini

1839
01:44:07,614 --> 01:44:09,449
kwa udanganyifu wa hisa wa mamilioni ya dola?

1840
01:44:09,484 --> 01:44:13,519
-Sawa, naapa sikuwa na ufahamu wowote
kuhusu haya yote uliyoyasema.

1841
01:44:20,528 --> 01:44:22,363
-Unatarajia niamini hivyo?

1842
01:44:22,398 --> 01:44:24,695
Wewe ni mkurugenzi mkuu.

1843
01:44:29,504 --> 01:44:35,035
♪♪

1844
01:44:35,070 --> 01:44:37,411
-Mkurugenzi mkuu mwenza.

1845
01:44:37,446 --> 01:44:39,809
<i>-Niambie kwa nini jambo hili haliwezi kusubiri</i>
<i>kwa wiki chache nyingine.</i>

1846
01:44:44,013 --> 01:44:51,788
-Nakuambia, Stan.

1847
01:44:51,823 --> 01:44:54,626
-Naelekea kituo cha wasafiri
sasa hivi.

1848
01:44:54,661 --> 01:44:56,760
<i>-Nini?</i>
-Hebu subiri kwanza.

1849
01:44:56,795 --> 01:44:58,124
-Nipo lango la saba. Uko wapi?

1850
01:44:58,159 --> 01:45:00,632
<i>-Unakimbia?</i>
-Hapana, Stan. Hapana, niko sawa.

1851
01:45:00,667 --> 01:45:02,029
Nakuambia, mimi --
niambie tu hilo lango.

1852
01:45:02,064 --> 01:45:05,835
<i>-Ninapanda</i>
<i>ndege hapa, Jim.</i>

1853
01:45:05,870 --> 01:45:09,938
-Sawa, nisikilize, Stan.

1854
01:45:09,973 --> 01:45:13,073
Haya, hili ndilo jambo kuu.

1855
01:45:13,108 --> 01:45:14,910
Simu laki tano za BlackBerry
kwa kampuni ya ATandT kwa dola sifuri.

1856
01:45:14,945 --> 01:45:17,616
<i>-Kuna ujanja gani?</i>
-Hapana. Hakuna ujanja.

1857
01:45:17,651 --> 01:45:20,047
Ni zako ikiwa uko tayari
kuzitoa kwa punguzo

1858
01:45:20,082 --> 01:45:24,458
mwezi mmoja kabla ya iPhone.

1859
01:45:24,493 --> 01:45:26,625
<i>-[Anashusha pumzi]</i>

1860
01:45:26,660 --> 01:45:30,398
-Stan, hebu bwana. Una deni langu.

1861
01:45:30,433 --> 01:45:32,092
Umeuza dakika nyingi
kwa sababu yetu.

1862
01:45:32,127 --> 01:45:35,403
<i>-Ndiyo, lakini unajua</i>
<i>shida ni nini</i>

1863
01:45:35,438 --> 01:45:38,670
<i>kuhusu kuuza dakika?</i>

1864
01:45:38,705 --> 01:45:40,639
-Nini?

1865
01:45:40,674 --> 01:45:42,872
<i>-Kuna dakika moja tu</i>
<i>ndani ya dakika moja.</i>

1866
01:45:42,907 --> 01:45:44,940
[Simu inakatika]

1867
01:45:44,975 --> 01:45:46,546
♪♪

1868
01:45:46,581 --> 01:45:49,846
♪♪

1869
01:45:49,881 --> 01:45:52,651
[Anapumua kwa nguvu]

1870
01:45:52,686 --> 01:46:01,187
[Simu ya mkononi inaita]

1871
01:46:01,222 --> 01:46:02,892
<i>-Halo.</i>
-Sawa, Mike, nisikilize.

1872
01:46:02,927 --> 01:46:06,929
Nadhani tuna
tatizo kubwa hapa.

1873
01:46:06,964 --> 01:46:09,932
Najua kile Apple wanachofanya.

1874
01:46:09,967 --> 01:46:11,604
<i>-Hatupaswi</i>
<i>kuzungumza kwenye simu.</i>

1875
01:46:11,639 --> 01:46:12,803
-Kwa nini?
-Eeh, tuko matatizoni.

1876
01:46:12,838 --> 01:46:14,167
<i>-Kwa nini?</i>
-Tuko matatizoni na Tume ya Hisa.

1877
01:46:14,202 --> 01:46:15,575
Lakini rudi haraka uwezavyo.

1878
01:46:15,610 --> 01:46:18,105
<i>Nina njia</i>
<i>ya kututoa katika hali hii.</i>

1879
01:46:18,140 --> 01:46:22,010
♪♪

1880
01:46:22,045 --> 01:46:25,684
♪♪

1881
01:46:25,719 --> 01:46:27,620
♪♪

1882
01:46:27,655 --> 01:46:35,859
[Kitambulisho kinatoa mlio]

1883
01:46:35,894 --> 01:46:44,131
♪♪

1884
01:46:44,166 --> 01:46:51,512
♪♪

1885
01:46:51,547 --> 01:46:53,580
-Habari.

1886
01:46:53,615 --> 01:47:00,851
Sawa, basi nisikilize.

1887
01:47:00,886 --> 01:47:09,090
ATandT wanajua vyema
kile wanachokifanya.

1888
01:47:09,125 --> 01:47:11,026
Walitaka Apple iwaundie
jitu linalokula data sana,

1889
01:47:11,061 --> 01:47:13,699
kwa sababu huko ndiko
wanakolipeleka soko.

1890
01:47:13,734 --> 01:47:16,999
Hawauzi dakika
tena, Mike.

1891
01:47:17,034 --> 01:47:19,870
Wanauza data.

1892
01:47:19,905 --> 01:47:21,740
-Amefika.

1893
01:47:21,775 --> 01:47:23,643
-Ni nani huyo?

1894
01:47:23,678 --> 01:47:27,042
-Wanakusubiri
kwenye chumba cha jirani.

1895
01:47:27,077 --> 01:47:32,179
-Nani --

1896
01:47:32,214 --> 01:47:34,049
Nini -- Ulifanya nini?

1897
01:47:35,855 --> 01:47:38,020
-Nimefanya makubaliano.

1898
01:47:40,156 --> 01:47:43,157
Tume itakupata wewe,

1899
01:47:43,192 --> 01:47:46,193
kiti chako cha bodi,
na ushirikiano wetu kamili

1900
01:47:46,228 --> 01:47:47,964
katika uchunguzi wao wa kijinai.

1901
01:47:47,999 --> 01:47:49,603
Na kwa ajili hiyo,
watatuacha bila kutusumbua.

1902
01:47:49,638 --> 01:47:51,869
♪♪

1903
01:47:51,904 --> 01:47:54,608
Na wanataka dola milioni 183.

1904
01:47:54,643 --> 01:47:57,809
♪♪

1905
01:47:57,844 --> 01:48:04,552
